<TR>
<TD colSpan=9>
<P align=center><strong>课程信息</strong></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>课程名称: English</strong><BR></TD>
<TD><BR></TD>
<TD><strong>上课日期</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2>April 3rd, 2010<BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2><strong>上课时长</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2>分钟<BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课对象</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2>Grade 4 <BR></TD>
<TD><strong>学生信息</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=5>21 students<BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=3><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ）</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=6><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N）</strong></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课目标<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>科学概念：<BR>过程与方法：<BR>情感、态度、价值观：</P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课内容</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>Main tasks: <BR>- Review of "Three Little Monkeys" <BR>- Review of "Is this your shirt?" <BR>- Learn to write an English poem<BR><BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课提纲<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>第一课时：<BR>What is your English name?（10mins) <BR>- Q by teacher and A by students <BR><BR>Review of "Three Little Monkeys" (10 mins) <BR>- Emphasize the difficult parts like the second line <BR>- Watch videos of last week <BR><BR>Sentences review and pair practice：(10 mins) <BR>- Is this your skirt? <BR>- Yes, it is. <BR>- No, it isn't. <BR>- Are those your pants? <BR>- Yes, they are. <BR>- I like my blue sweater. <BR>- My yellow shirt is too small. <BR><BR>Game: What do you want to wear today? (10mins) <BR>- show the pictures of wears <BR>- select students to choose their favourite wears <BR><BR>Poem appreciation <BR>5.1 Meaning of the poem: (10 mins) <BR>Seasons <BR>Spring is green， <BR>Summer is bright， <BR>Autumn is gold， <BR>Winter is white. <BR>Year in year out， <BR>We work and fight， <BR>For a new world， <BR>of red sunlight<BR><BR>第二课时：<BR><BR>5.2 Try to read the poem: (10 mins) <BR><BR>Structure of an English poem: (10 mins) <BR>Spring, Spring, Spring, <BR>Lovely Spring, <BR>Sweet Spring. <BR>Spring is beautiful, <BR>Spring is bird's singing. <BR>Oh, I love you, my Spring. <BR><BR>Write an English poem（20 mins) <BR><BR>Selected students to read their poems ：(10 mins)</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>教学环境、材料需求</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>N/A</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>助教需求<BR></strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>YES<BR><BR></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE><BR></P>
<P><BR>&nbsp;</P>
<div class="hdwiki_tmml">&nbsp;第三次活动</div>
<P>
<TABLE class=table width="100%" align=left>
<TBODY>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=9>
<P align=center><strong>上课准备提纲</strong></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=9>
<P align=center><strong>志愿者信息</strong></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>备课人</strong></TD>
<TD><BR>小怀</TD>
<TD><strong>Email/MSN</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=3><BR><A href="mailto:ytliyuhui@126.com">ytliyuhui@126.com</A></TD>
<TD colSpan=2><strong>所属课程组</strong><BR></TD>
<TD><BR>English</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=9>
<P align=center><strong>课程信息</strong></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>课程名称</strong><BR></TD>
<TD><BR>English</TD>
<TD><strong>上课日期</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2><BR>April 10th 2010</TD>
<TD colSpan=2><strong>上课时长</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2>100分钟<BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课对象</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2><BR>Grade4</TD>
<TD><strong>学生信息</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=5><BR>28 students</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=3><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ）</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=6><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N）</strong></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课目标<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>科学概念：<BR>过程与方法：首先复习之前学过内容，讲解单复数及人称变化。介绍复活节，及复活节寻彩蛋游戏，教授复活节有关词汇。根据Easter Egg Hunt改遍游戏分组进行，回答问题集齐印章，过程中复习教授内容。各组完成任务后拿到一个单词，最后组成一句励志谚语。<BR>情感、态度、价值观：使孩子了解西方复活节，并通过“复活”的意义培养一种不放弃不丧失希望的精神。</P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课内容</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>1.Review of "this is/these are" ," plural noun forms", "am;is;are"</P>
<P>2.The rules of the plural of nouns</P>
<P>3.What's "Easter" and "Easter Egg Hunt"</P>
<P>4.Learn some words about "Easter"</P>
<P>5.Games, then teach several new words to form a proverb</P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课提纲<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>第一课时：</P>
<P>Warm up(5mins):</P>
<P>-Self introduction and greeting</P>
<P>Review of the usage of "am; is; are"(8mins):</P>
<P>-explain the usage</P>
<P>-Short sentence translation</P>
<P>-Q &amp; A</P>
<P>Review of " plural noun forms"(10mins):</P>
<P>-jackets, shorts, sweaters,shirts, skirts,dresses, pants, socks etc.</P>
<P>-Some new words</P>
<P>-Different groups of plural nouns</P>
<P>Explain the rules of the plurals of the nouns(10mins)</P>
<P>What's Easter and words related(15mins)</P>
<P>-Origin, custom, date,flower etc.</P>
<P>-Easter, rabbit, Easter egg, Easter egg hunt, lily, Jesus etc.</P>
<P>-Q: Tell me what you konw about the Easter?<BR><BR>第二课时：</P>
<P>Explain the rules of the "Easter egg hunt" and our game(8mins)</P>
<P>-Divided into 7 groups, each has 4 kids</P>
<P>Game:(the rest of time)</P>
<P>-three groups of assistants with questions</P>
<P>-every&nbsp;groups of students&nbsp;should pass through them and everyone should answer 3 questions(or paragraph translation,team work)</P>
<P>-each correct answer will be awarded with a little pattern from the assistant</P>
<P>-when everyone of the group has collected 3 patterns, they can get a word from me and learn how to read</P>
<P>-after each group gets the word, we form a sentence with&nbsp;these words and learn how to read it</P>
<P>-the meaning will be told next week<BR><BR></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>教学环境、材料需求</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>1、pictures<BR>2、questions<BR>3、words</P>
<P>as beautiful as possible<BR></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>助教需求<BR></strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>at least 7</TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></P>
<P><BR></P>
<P><BR><BR><BR><BR>&nbsp; </P>
