<TD colSpan=5>25 students<BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=3><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ）</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=6><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N）</strong></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课目标<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>科学概念：<BR>过程与方法：<BR>情感、态度、价值观：</P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课内容</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>-Review of verbs</P>
<P>-否定句和疑问句</P>
<P>-Learn a song<BR></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课提纲<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>第一课时：</P>
<P>Meaning of "While there is life, there is hope"(5 mins)</P>
<P>-Encouragement</P>
<P>Warm up-Simon says(10 mins)</P>
<P>-rules</P>
<P>-stand up/sit down/ open(close) the door(your eyes), touch, clean the blackboad/ show me/clap(raise) your hands</P>
<P>-正/反做</P>
<P>Review of verbs(20 mins)</P>
<P>-put on/ take off/ fold/ hang up/ wash/ put away/ eat/ drink/ run/ jump/ </P>
<P>-TPR， 分组练习，比赛猜词</P>
<P>否定，疑问句（15mins)</P>
<P>- Are you a boy/Can you show me your pencil?/Do you like music?/Is your coat blue?</P>
<P>-全部肯定回答/全部否定回答/根据实际情况回答<BR><BR><BR>第二课时：</P>
<P>Listen to the song and complet the lyric(8 mins)</P>
<P>Explaination and learn to read(10 mins)</P>
<P>Watch the video and learn to act(10 mins)</P>
<P>Divided into groups and practise with assistant teachers(15 mins)</P>
<P>Act<BR><BR></P></TD></TR>
