<P align=center><strong>课程信息</strong></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>课程名称</strong><BR></TD>
<TD>Zhen Hua Unit 8 Children's day<BR></TD>
<TD><strong>上课日期</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2><BR>29 May</TD>
<TD colSpan=2><strong>上课时长</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2>80 分钟<BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课对象</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2><BR>Grade 4</TD>
<TD><strong>学生信息</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=5><BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=3><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ）</strong><BR>Y</TD>
<TD colSpan=6>
<P><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N）</strong><strong>N</strong></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课目标<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>继续增强孩子们使用口语的能力，培养情景对话的能力。</P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课内容</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>1) Oral enhancement <BR></P>
<P>2) Children’s day / Poem for family <BR></P>
<P>3) English song <BR></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课提纲<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>第一课时：Warm up talk (5 mins) <BR>T: Where are you from? <BR>T: Which sports do you like? <BR>S: I like basketball, table tennis, soccer, volleyball, badminton swimming, jumping, <BR>T: Do you like fruit? <BR>S: Yes I do. <BR>T: What fruits do you like best? <BR>S: I like apples, pears, bananas, oranges, strawberries, watermelons, peaches <BR><BR>Try to make self-introduction. (10 mins) <BR>Good morning everyone. My name is XX. I’m XX years old. I’m from XX province. I like singing, dancing, reading, Surfing. I want to say nice to meet you here. It’s so nice to know you. I hope we can make friends. (I hope we can be friends) <BR><BR>Country / City review (5 mins) <BR>T: Remember the country we learned last time? Let’s review a little bit <BR>What is the capital of China? <BR>China - Beijing <BR>UK - London <BR>Russia - Moscow <BR>Egypt - Cairo <BR>Australia - Sydney <BR><BR>New words <BR>France – Paris <BR>America – Washington DC <BR>A poem on family (20 mins) <BR><BR>T: What date is today? S: Today is Saturday. <BR>T: What festival will it be on 1 June? <BR>S: It’s children’s day. <BR>T: Ah, yes it’s our holiday. <BR></P>
<P>Poem: <BR>Father, mother and I <BR>I have a sweet home <BR>Thank you for always being there, (谢谢你们一直在这里） <BR>And showing me that you really care. （让我知道你们真的很关心我） <BR>Sometimes I am lovely - lovely . <BR>Sometimes I am naughty-naughty <BR>But don't have to worry (但是不用为我担心) <BR>I know what I am doing 我知道我在做什么 <BR>Father and mother爸爸妈妈 <BR>I love you我爱你们 <BR>Always and forever(一直到永远) <BR><BR><BR><BR><BR>第二课时：English Song</P>
<P><BR>Edelweiss, Edelweiss <BR>Every morning you greet me <BR>Small and white, clean and bright <BR>You look happy to meet me <BR><BR>Blossom of snow may you bloom and grow <BR>Bloom and grow forever <BR><BR>Edelweiss, Edelweiss <BR>Bless my homeland forever <BR>Small and white, clean and bright <BR>You look happy to meet me <BR><BR>Blossom of snow may you bloom and grow <BR>Bloom and grow forever <BR><BR>Edelweiss, edelweiss <BR>Bless my homeland forever <BR><BR></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>教学环境、材料需求</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>1、小音箱，可以放歌的。<BR>2、<BR>3、<BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>助教需求<BR></strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>N/A</TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></P>
