<P><BR><BR><BR><BR>&nbsp; </P>
<div class="hdwiki_tmml">第二次</div>
<TABLE class=table width="100%" align=left>
<TBODY>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=9>
<P align=center><strong>上课准备提纲</strong></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=9>
<P align=center><strong>志愿者信息</strong></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>备课人</strong><BR></TD>
<TD>小黑小红</TD>
<TD><strong>Email/MSN</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=3><A href="mailto:shenbeibettina@163.com">shenbeibettina@163.com</A></TD>
<TD colSpan=2><strong>所属课程组</strong><BR></TD>
<TD>英语组</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=9>
<P align=center><strong>课程信息</strong></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>课程名称</strong><BR></TD>
<TD>Our Classroom</TD>
<TD><strong>上课日期</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2><BR>9.18</TD>
<TD colSpan=2><strong>上课时长</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2>两堂课<BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课对象</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2><BR>振华 四年级 普通班</TD>
<TD><strong>学生信息</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=5>18人，其中三名男生<BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=3><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ）Y</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=6><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N） N</strong></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课目标<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>主要复习Unit 1 和Unit 2</P>
<P>熟练掌握Stationery和Classroom等相关单词，并进行简单问答</P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课内容</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>Warm up &amp; Review 1:</P>
<P>i&nbsp; One word on Stationery per student without repeat. And write them on the blackboard.</P>
<P>pen, pencil, pencil-case, eraser, ruler, textbook, story-book, math book , Chinese book , crayon, English book , notebook, sharpener, chalk, stapler</P>
<P>ii&nbsp; T: ……(describe a certain situation), what do I need?</P>
<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;S: (You need) a/an……</P>
<P>iii&nbsp; One Student: ……, what do I need?</P>
<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Other students:……</P>
<P>iiii Game</P>
<P>选一名同学来找文具，先背对大家；大家选出一个文具如pencil，放在某个同学的抽屉里；猜的同学转身，开始找pencil，其他同学同时读pencil；当这个同学离目标物越来越近时，同学们就更大声的说pencil；反之，声音变小；最后，猜的同学确定pencil具体方位。</P>
<P>Lead in: <BR>Where are we? We're in the classroom.&nbsp; [适当扩展Room: bed room, washroom, waiting room etc]</P>
<P>What can we&nbsp;see inside the classroom?/ Wow, so many things in this classroom.</P>
<P>Focused Teaching:</P>
<P>Key words: door, window, desk, chair, wall, floor,&nbsp;light, fan,blackboard, flag, map, picture</P>
<P>讲解每个单词</P>
<P>【助教】辅导</P>
<P>Practice: 情景表演（描述教室）建议助教扮演大人角色一组5-6人，尽量每位同学都有练习到（场景相见纸条，分组抽）(可能会用到的Adj: big, small, large, bright, clean, dirty, white……)</P>
<P>i 开家长会前，Papa: I don't know which is your classroom? S: ……</P>
<P>ii 家中&nbsp; Parents: How is your new classroom? S: Yes/No,……</P>
<P>iii 迎接新同学 Welcome to our new school</P>
<P>iiii Cats</P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P>相关动作：</P>
<P>open the door, close the window, turn on the light, clean the blackboard, draw a picture, sweep the floor</P>
<P>【助教】辅导</P>
<P>Game: 单词接龙</P>
<P>老师先说一个单词如door, 迅速指向另一个同学，该同学也说出一个单词（不与上重复）并指向下一个同学，哪个同学卡壳（超过5秒）就输了。该游戏进行三轮，共有三位同学failed.</P>
<P>小小惩罚环节：</P>
<P>老师向一个小朋友（刚刚游戏失败的）出示一张纸，上面写有动作指令如sweep the floor，该同学执行该指令，其他同学猜。</P>
<P>Review2:</P>
<P>Shape: What shape is it? It's round, oval, triangle, rectangle, square, cross, star, heart……</P>
<P>找找生活中是这些形状的物品，加深印象</P>
<P>若时间允许，最后增加一个解圈子的团体游戏</P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课提纲<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>教学环境、材料需求</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>1、<BR>2、<BR>3、<BR></TD></TR>
