<tr>
<td><strong>授课目标<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8">学会介绍自己的Family；掌握How many people are there in your family之类的句型</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课内容</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8"><br>Topic—Meet My Family <br><br>【1】Greeting <br><br>【2】Review（15min） <br>以小游戏“飞行棋”的形式展开，复习之前课程的主要内容 <br>最后一步，引入Family话题。 <br><br>【3】Focused Teaching 1 <br>i family, father, mother, grandfather, grandmother, aunt, uncle, brother, sister etc (10min) <br><br>Practice <br>Family Tree (15min) <br>简单介绍Family Tree。在助教老师的辅导下，每位同学画一个Family Tree，并简单描述。选出4至6位小朋友在讲台前来描述自己的Family。 <br><br>ii Extended Practice（20min--10min Intro&amp;learning;10min describing） <br>Describe the Simpsons (Picture should be prepared) <br>Key Points: <br>Homer—fat, Marge—blue hair, Bart—10/naughty, Lisa—8/smart, Maggie—3/baby. <br><br>【4】Focused Teaching 2（10min） <br>How many people are there in your family? <br>Numbers:1,2……13,14,15 <br><br>i How many apples are there on the tree? <br>随意往大树上加苹果的图片，一问一答。小朋友们自主练习。 <br><br>ii 随意拿出小朋友们之前画的Family Tree的图，问“How many people are there in Tom’s family?” <br>Example--A：How many people are there in your family？ <br>B：…… <br>A：Who are they? <br>B：…… <br><br><br><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课提纲<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8"></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>教学环境、材料需求</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8">1、飞行棋复习版块，需提前写好有小问题的小纸片，背扣着并贴到黑板上<br>2、The Simpsons 的图片<br>3、<br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>助教需求<br></strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8">
<p>N/A</p>
<p>约需4名助教老师</p></td></tr></tbody></table>
