<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>志愿者信息</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>备课人</strong></td>
<td>&nbsp; &nbsp; 采薇 &nbsp; &nbsp;</td>
<td><b>整理</b></td><td colspan="3">含笑幻子</td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>所属课程组</strong></td>
<td>美术组</td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>课程信息</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>课程名称</strong></td>
<td>纸杯娃娃</td>
<td><strong>上课日期</strong></td>
<td colspan="2"><br></td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>上课时长</strong></td>
<td colspan="2">100分钟</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课对象</strong></td>
<td colspan="2">1~6年级</td>
<td><strong>学生信息</strong></td>
<td colspan="5"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="3"><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ）</strong></td>
<td colspan="6"><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N）</strong></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课目标</strong></td>
<td colspan="8">
<p>1 锻炼学生的动手能力,观察力,想象力.</p><p>2 激发对美术和手工的兴趣</p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课内容</strong></td><td colspan="8">1 教授纸杯娃娃的几个做法<br><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课提纲<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8"><br>1 向学生介绍纸杯娃娃.并看几张纸杯娃娃的图片0'~10'<br><br>2 主讲介绍纸杯娃娃的做法.10'~20'<br><br>3 分发工具<br>1) 纸杯.剪刀.水彩笔.彩色纸<br>
<br>4 助教协助,学生发挥自己的想象,做自己的纸杯娃娃.上色 20'~70<br>
<br>5 再做一个送给朋友的纸杯娃娃 70'~95'<br>
<br>6&nbsp;</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>教学环境、材料需求</strong></td>
<td colspan="8">纸杯:一人两个<br>彩色纸:一组5张<br>剪刀<br>铅笔<br>尺子<br>胶水 双面胶 透明胶布<br>彩色笔<br>纸杯娃娃图片<br><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>助教需求</strong></td>
<td colspan="8">按照助教与学生1:3的比例征集助教<br>提前熟知制作过程,给予指导<br>记录学生表现<br>保证安全<br>维持负责的学生纪律,掌控绘画进度,增强动手能力<br>协调与独立制作. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>
<div class="img img_l" style="width: 29px; "><a href="uploads/201204/1334685682mRptB3Vs.jpg" target="_blank" title="纸杯娃娃"><img src="uploads/201204/1334685682mRptB3Vs_s.jpg" alt="纸杯娃娃" title="纸杯娃娃"></a><strong>纸杯娃娃</strong></div>
