<TD><strong>授课目标<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>科学概念：<BR>过程与方法：<BR>情感、态度、价值观：</P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课内容</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8><BR>1.Reviewing.对上节课的有关句型：What time is it?/It's time to.... <BR><BR>2.教授本节课句型和单词。（见“知识目标”相关内容） <BR><BR>3. 制作环节（助教帮助）.利用彩笔、剪刀、纸张等工具画出自己喜欢的服饰,之后用胶带粘贴到黑板上。 <BR><BR>4.剧目表演. <BR><BR>A.Wow,so many colors! <BR><BR>But where is my skirt/T-shirt...? <BR><BR>B.Is this your skirt/T-shirt...? <BR><BR>A.No,it's not. <BR><BR>B. What color is it? <BR><BR>A.Blue/Red/Purple <BR><BR>B.Let me find it,oh,it's here. <BR><BR>A.Tank you. <BR><BR>B.Look,whose T-shirt is it? <BR><BR>It's beautiful. <BR><BR>Oh,it's John's/Lily's. <BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课提纲<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>第一课时：复习上节课的内容（5分钟左右）；教授新的句型和单词<BR><BR><BR>第二课时：利用彩笔绘画；进行对话表演（在制作的图片基础上）<BR><BR></TD></TR>
