<TR>
<TD><strong>课程名称</strong><BR></TD>
<TD><BR>sing together！</TD>
<TD><strong>上课日期</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2><BR>2010/4/17</TD>
<TD colSpan=2><strong>上课时长</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2>120分钟<BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课对象</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2><BR>育才四年级学生</TD>
<TD><strong>学生信息</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=5>5人 四年级<BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=3><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ）</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=6><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N）</strong></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课目标<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>科学概念：<BR>过程与方法：<BR>情感、态度、价值观：</P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课内容</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8><BR>1.Reviewing，以电脑图片的方式展示上节课学习的部分与衣服相关的单词，比如Jacket，coat,T-shirt等，一定程度上也让孩子形象地认识这些衣服，纠正单纯教授时对于服饰概念的抽象认识。 <BR><BR>2。sing together！教授英文歌曲《the wheels on the bus》.首先带领孩子们通晓不会的单词和句子，并了解整篇文章的中文翻译；然后对照电脑视频、主讲领唱的方式学习歌曲。歌词如下： <BR><BR>Lyrics <BR>"The Wheels on the Bus" <BR>The wheels on the bus go round and round, <BR>round and round, <BR>round and round. <BR>The wheels on the bus go round and round, <BR>all through the town. <BR>(Roll hands around each other) <BR>The wipers on the bus go Swish, swish, swish; <BR>Swish, swish, swish; <BR>Swish, swish, swish. <BR>The wipers on the bus go Swish, swish, swish, <BR>all through the town. <BR>("Swish" hands in front of you like windshield wipers) <BR>The horn on the bus goes Beep, beep, beep; <BR>Beep, beep, beep; <BR>Beep, beep, beep. <BR>The horn on the bus goes Beep, beep, beep, <BR>all through the town. <BR>(Slap palm in front of you like honking a horn) <BR>The doors on the bus go open and shut; <BR>Open and shut; <BR>Open and shut. <BR>The doors on the bus go open and shut; <BR>all through the town. <BR>(Push hands back and forth in front of you) <BR>The Driver on the bus says "Move on back, <BR>move on back, move on back;" <BR>The Driver on the bus says "Move on back", <BR>all through the town. <BR>(Point thumb over your shoulder) <BR>The babies on the bus says "Wee, wee, wee; <BR>Wee, wee, wee; <BR>Wee, wee, wee". <BR>The babies on the bus says "Wee, wee, wee", <BR>all through the town. <BR>(Rub fists in front of eyes) <BR>The mommies on the bus says "Shh, shh, shh; <BR>Shh, shh, shh; <BR>Shh, shh, shh." <BR>The mommies on the bus says "Shh, shh, shh" <BR>all through the town. <BR>(Hold index finger in front of mouth as if saying shhh) <BR><BR>NEW WORDS: <BR>Wheels 车轮 <BR>Round 旋转，绕圈 <BR>Wipers 雨刷 <BR>Swish 嗖嗖声 <BR>Horn 喇叭 <BR>Beep 嘟嘟声 <BR>shut 关门 <BR>Shh 嘘，别出声 <BR><BR>3.在黑板上画出播放器的模型，让孩子们分别指示快放、慢放、暂停等按钮来控制歌曲的节奏，体会其中乐趣。临近下课时，孩子们和主讲、助教一起唱这首歌曲。 <BR><BR><BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课提纲<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>第一课时：复习上节课内容，并对比一些图片进行补充，教会孩子们单词中的生词<BR><BR><BR>第二课时：看视频学歌曲并配合动作表演；游戏环节<BR><BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>教学环境、材料需求</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>1、<BR>2、<BR>3、<BR></TD></TR>
