<P>科学概念：轻松教学<BR>过程与方法：复习第三单元内容和上节课歌曲<BR>情感、态度、价值观：</P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课内容</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>1、单词复习： <BR>（1） Jacket,&nbsp;shirt,&nbsp;T-shirt,&nbsp;sweater,&nbsp;pants,&nbsp;jeans,&nbsp;socks,&nbsp;shoes,&nbsp;shorts,&nbsp;skirt,&nbsp;dress,&nbsp;vest,&nbsp;cap,&nbsp;hat&nbsp;&nbsp; <BR>（2） White,&nbsp;black,&nbsp;blue,&nbsp;green,&nbsp;gray,&nbsp;pink,&nbsp;brown, red, yellow,purple </P>
<P>2、A&nbsp;Poem&nbsp; <BR>Seasons&nbsp; <BR>Spring&nbsp;is&nbsp;green，&nbsp; <BR>Summer&nbsp;is&nbsp;bright，&nbsp; <BR>Autumn&nbsp;is&nbsp;gold，&nbsp; <BR>Winter&nbsp;is&nbsp;white.&nbsp; <BR>Year&nbsp;in&nbsp;year&nbsp;out，&nbsp; <BR>We&nbsp;work&nbsp;and&nbsp;fight，&nbsp; <BR>For&nbsp;a&nbsp;new&nbsp;world，&nbsp; <BR>of&nbsp;red&nbsp;sunlight </P>
<P>3、句型复习： <BR>(1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;This&nbsp;is&nbsp;my/her/his&nbsp;sweater.&nbsp; <BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;What&nbsp;color&nbsp;is&nbsp;it？&nbsp;It&nbsp;is&nbsp;white.&nbsp; <BR>(2)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Is&nbsp;this&nbsp;your&nbsp;skirt?&nbsp;Yes,&nbsp;it&nbsp;is.&nbsp;No,&nbsp;it&nbsp;isn't.&nbsp; <BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Are&nbsp;these&nbsp;your&nbsp;socks?&nbsp; <BR>(3)&nbsp;&nbsp;Whose&nbsp;pants&nbsp;are&nbsp;these?&nbsp;They&nbsp;are&nbsp;Peter's.&nbsp; <BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Whose&nbsp;cap&nbsp;is&nbsp;it?&nbsp;It's&nbsp;lily's.&nbsp; <BR>(4)&nbsp;&nbsp;Today,&nbsp;I'm&nbsp;wearing&nbsp;red&nbsp;sweater&nbsp;and&nbsp;black&nbsp;jeans.&nbsp; </P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课提纲<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>第一课时：复习第三单元</P>
<P>1、用提问的方式复习衣服和颜色单词。</P>
<P>2、学首有季节和颜色的诗</P>
<P>3、启发学生用单词介绍自己穿的衣服，引入句型。<BR><BR><BR>第二课时：</P>
<P>3、"Whose&nbsp;clothing"&nbsp; <BR><BR>准备一些衣服的图片，每位同学选一套衣服的图片。两位同学一组。 <BR><BR>用所选衣服图片组对话，其中要用到上节课所学到的句型。 <BR>4、读诗、唱歌"Seasons","Apple Red","The&nbsp;Wheels&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;Bus" <BR><BR></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>教学环境、材料需求</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>1、以上内容根据学生的接受能力进行删减和增加<BR>2、四年级课本<BR>3、<BR></TD></TR>
