<TD colSpan=2>分钟<BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课对象</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2>Grade 4</TD>
<TD><strong>学生信息</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=5>5-7 students<BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=3><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ） Not yet</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=6><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N） No</strong></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课目标<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>Subject:&nbsp; Mother's Day</P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课内容</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>1. Review</P>
<P>2. What can you do for your Mom on Mother's Day?</P>
<P>3. English Song: I Love My Mommy</P>
<P>4.&nbsp;Make a&nbsp;gift for Mom.</P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课提纲<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>第一课时：</P>
<P>-Review </P>
<P>Poem</P>
<P>Seasons <BR>Spring is green， <BR>Summer is bright， <BR>Autumn is gold， <BR>Winter is white. <BR>Year in year out， <BR>We work and fight， <BR>For a new world， <BR>of red sunlight </P>
<P>-Introduce Mother's Day</P>
<P>Q: What can you do for your mom on Mother's Day?</P>
<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Can you ***** for your mom on Mother's Day?</P>
<P>Phrases for answer options:</P>
<P>mop the floor <BR>wash the dishes <BR>make the bed <BR>sweep the floor <BR>water the plant <BR>wash the clothes <BR>clean the windows <BR>fold the clothes <BR>cook dinner <BR>go shopping with<BR></P>
<P>-Phrase Practice</P>
<P>&nbsp; Game -- Guess what's he/she doing!</P>
<P>-Sentence Practice</P>
<P>&nbsp; Y/N Questions exercise and interaction with Teaching Assistants.</P>
<P>&nbsp; Game -- Mutual Interview and write down the result.</P>
<P><BR><BR>第二课时：</P>
<P>- New Song: &nbsp;I Love My Mommy</P>
<P>Lyrics: </P>
<P>I love you mommy. Happy Mother's Day.</P>
<P>I love my mommy. I go shopping with her.</P>
<P>I water plants with her. I love my mommy.</P>
<P>I love my mommy. I go shopping with her. <BR><BR>I water plants with her. I love my mommy. </P>
<P>I love my mommy. I fold clothes with her.</P>
<P>I wash dishes with her. I love my mommy.</P>
<P>I love you mommy. Happy Mother's Day!</P>
<P>- Make a gift for Mom</P>
