<TD><strong>授课目标<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>科学概念：<BR>过程与方法：<BR>情感、态度、价值观：</P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课内容</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>1 review the poem "Seasons" </P>
<P>Spring&nbsp;is&nbsp;green，&nbsp;&nbsp; Summer&nbsp;is&nbsp;bright，&nbsp;&nbsp; Autumn&nbsp;is&nbsp;gold，&nbsp;&nbsp; Winter&nbsp;is&nbsp;white.&nbsp;&nbsp; </P>
<P>Year&nbsp;in&nbsp;year&nbsp;out，&nbsp;&nbsp; We&nbsp;work&nbsp;and&nbsp;fight，&nbsp;&nbsp; For&nbsp;a&nbsp;new&nbsp;world，&nbsp;&nbsp; of&nbsp;red&nbsp;sunlight&nbsp; <BR></P>
<P>2 What's the weather like today? </P>
<P>2 It's sunny,snowy,windy,cloudy. </P>
<P>3 I feel cold,cool,hot,warm,fresh </P>
<P>4 review the words of cloth:&nbsp;&nbsp;Jacket,&nbsp;shirt,&nbsp;T-shirt,&nbsp;sweater,&nbsp;pants,&nbsp;jeans,&nbsp;socks,&nbsp;shoes,&nbsp;shorts,&nbsp;skirt,&nbsp;dress,&nbsp;vest,&nbsp;</P>
<P>cap,&nbsp;hat&nbsp;&nbsp;</P>
<P>4 I'm wearing pink shirt and blue pants. </P>
<P>5 counting: one,two,three,four,five,six,seven,eight,nine,ten,eleven,twelve,thirteen...</P>
<P>6 How much is this skirt? How much are these pants? </P>
<P>7 a new song: Twinkle&nbsp;twinkle&nbsp;little&nbsp;star<BR><BR></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课提纲<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>第一课时：复习所学内容</P>
<P>复习学过的诗，引出问天气，买衣服。<BR><BR><BR>第二课时：singing a new song</P>
<P>Twinkle&nbsp;twinkle&nbsp;little&nbsp;star，&nbsp; How&nbsp;I&nbsp;wonder&nbsp;what&nbsp;you&nbsp;are；&nbsp; <BR>Up&nbsp;above&nbsp;the&nbsp;world&nbsp;so&nbsp;high,&nbsp; Like&nbsp;a&nbsp;diamond&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;sky；&nbsp; <BR>Twinkle&nbsp;twinkle&nbsp;little&nbsp;star，&nbsp; How&nbsp;I&nbsp;wonder&nbsp;what&nbsp;you&nbsp;are。&nbsp; </P>
<P>In&nbsp;the&nbsp;dark&nbsp;blue&nbsp;sky&nbsp;you&nbsp;keep,&nbsp; Often&nbsp;through&nbsp;my&nbsp;curtain&nbsp;peep；&nbsp; <BR>Twinkle&nbsp;twinkle&nbsp;all&nbsp;the&nbsp;night, Till&nbsp;the&nbsp;sun&nbsp;is&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;sky；&nbsp; <BR>Twinkle&nbsp;twinkle&nbsp;little&nbsp;star，&nbsp; How&nbsp;I&nbsp;wonder&nbsp;what&nbsp;you&nbsp;are&nbsp; <BR></P>
<P>Twinkle&nbsp;twinkle&nbsp;little&nbsp;star，&nbsp;一闪一闪小星星&nbsp; <BR>Twinkle:&nbsp;vi.&nbsp;闪亮。n.&nbsp;闪光 <BR>Wonder：How&nbsp;I&nbsp;wonder&nbsp;what&nbsp;you&nbsp;are；我多想知道你是什么&nbsp; <BR>vi&nbsp;/&nbsp;vt:&nbsp;想知道，对~感到疑惑&nbsp; <BR>Up&nbsp;above&nbsp;the&nbsp;world&nbsp;so&nbsp;high,&nbsp;挂在天空那么高&nbsp; <BR>Above:&nbsp;prep.在~正上方，超过，超出&nbsp; <BR>Like&nbsp;a&nbsp;diamond&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;sky；&nbsp;就像一颗颗钻石挂在天空&nbsp; <BR>Diamond：钻石，菱形&nbsp; <BR>Twinkle&nbsp;twinkle&nbsp;little&nbsp;star，&nbsp;一闪一闪小星星&nbsp; <BR>How&nbsp;I&nbsp;wonder&nbsp;what&nbsp;you&nbsp;are。&nbsp;我多想知道你是什么&nbsp; <BR><BR>In&nbsp;the&nbsp;dark&nbsp;blue&nbsp;sky&nbsp;you&nbsp;keep,&nbsp;你挂在深蓝色的天空&nbsp; <BR><BR>vt.保持，保存&nbsp; <BR>Often&nbsp;through&nbsp;my&nbsp;curtain&nbsp;peep；&nbsp;透过我的窗帘你若隐若现&nbsp; <BR>through:&nbsp;prep.在~之中，在~各处&nbsp; <BR>curtain:&nbsp;窗帘，帷幕&nbsp; <BR>peep:&nbsp;vi.偷看，隐现&nbsp;n.嘟嘟声&nbsp; <BR>Twinkle&nbsp;twinkle&nbsp;all&nbsp;the&nbsp;night,&nbsp;整夜整夜地闪烁呀&nbsp; <BR>Till&nbsp;the&nbsp;sun&nbsp;is&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;sky；&nbsp;直到太阳升上了天空&nbsp; <BR>Twinkle&nbsp;twinkle&nbsp;little&nbsp;star，一闪一闪小星星&nbsp; <BR>How&nbsp;I&nbsp;wonder&nbsp;what&nbsp;you&nbsp;are..&nbsp;我多想知道你是什么&nbsp; </P></TD></TR>
