<TD colSpan=9>
<P align=center><strong>课程信息</strong></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>课程名称</strong><BR></TD>
<TD>Shapes</TD>
<TD><strong>上课日期</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2>27.3</TD>
<TD colSpan=2><strong>上课时长</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2>50分钟 X 2（9:40-11:40/13:30-15:30）<BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课对象</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2>四五六年级</TD>
<TD><strong>学生信息</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=5>小班（约15人，四五年纪）/大班（约22人，五六年纪）</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=3><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况 &nbsp; &nbsp; Yes</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=6><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;No</strong></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课目标<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>掌握英语中各种形状的表达，并在生活中灵活运用；<BR>大胆表达<BR></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课内容</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>注：大小班具体授课内容有所差异。<BR><BR>&nbsp;【Review&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Warming&nbsp;up】<BR>i&nbsp;各个身体部位：head,&nbsp;finger,&nbsp;hand,&nbsp;arm,&nbsp;shoulder,&nbsp;leg,&nbsp;foot/feet,&nbsp;knee,&nbsp;toe etc.<BR>ii 听口令做动作:clap&nbsp;your&nbsp;hands/shake&nbsp;your&nbsp;hands/nod&nbsp;your&nbsp;heads/blink&nbsp;your&nbsp;eyes/bend&nbsp;your&nbsp;knees/pat&nbsp;your&nbsp;bellies/twist&nbsp;your&nbsp;shoulders/stamp&nbsp;your&nbsp;feet&nbsp;etc.<BR><BR>&nbsp;【Leading&nbsp;in】<BR>&nbsp;请小朋友分成两组在黑板上作画：the&nbsp;classroom&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;the&nbsp;playground<BR><BR>&nbsp;【Focused&nbsp;Teaching】<BR>i&nbsp;根据黑板上的画来介绍各种各样的形状Shapes:&nbsp;circle/square/triangle/rectangle/star/heart/oval/cross<BR>讲解（需借助提前准备的图片）<BR><BR>ii&nbsp;句型介绍：<BR>①The&nbsp;clock&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;circle./The&nbsp;book&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;rectangle.<BR>②I&nbsp;have&nbsp;a/an…….&nbsp;It’s…….<BR>对话介绍：<BR>-What&nbsp;the&nbsp;shape&nbsp;is&nbsp;it/the&nbsp;flag?<BR>-It’s……<BR><BR>&nbsp;【Practice&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Feedback】<BR>i&nbsp;由助教老师辅导小朋友们掌握各种形状的单词以及对话<BR>ii&nbsp;单词、句型以及对话练习<BR>①连线：<BR>NO.1&nbsp;图形与英文名，NO.&nbsp;2&nbsp;具体物体与英文名<BR>②老师与小朋友<BR>③小朋友与小朋友<BR><BR>&nbsp;【Free&nbsp;Practice&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Game】<BR><BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课提纲<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>第一课时：<BR><BR><BR>第二课时：<BR><BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>教学环境、材料需求</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>1、图片/卡片<BR>2、透明胶<BR>3、<BR></TD></TR>
