<td><strong>授课目标<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8">
<p>&nbsp;在母亲节说出你的爱！</p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课内容</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8">【Review】<br>
借助“飞行棋”以及助教老师的参与来复习前5次课讲的主要内容<br>
<br>
需提前准备好卡片和透明胶<br>
<br>
【Leading&nbsp;in】<br>
It’s&nbsp;Mother’s&nbsp;Day&nbsp;today!<br>
What&nbsp;can&nbsp;you&nbsp;do&nbsp;for&nbsp;your&nbsp;mom&nbsp;on&nbsp;Mother’s&nbsp;Day?<br>
Your&nbsp;ideas!<br>
（关于母亲节部分借鉴2010年春季朝阳育才Sofia主讲的一堂课）<br><br>&nbsp;【Focused&nbsp;Learning】<br>
1&nbsp;make&nbsp;the&nbsp;bed/sweep&nbsp;the&nbsp;floor/clean&nbsp;the&nbsp;windows/wash&nbsp;the&nbsp;clothes/cook&nbsp;the&nbsp;dinner/go&nbsp;shopping&nbsp;with&nbsp;her&nbsp;etc<br>
2&nbsp;助教老师辅导掌握<br>
<br>
【Free&nbsp;Practice】<br>
Guess:<br>
What&nbsp;he/she&nbsp;is&nbsp;doing?<br>
He/she&nbsp;is<br>
<br>
【Do-it-yourself】<br>在简易贺卡上写下想对妈妈说的话<br>
<br>
需提前准备好空白贺卡、彩笔<br><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课提纲<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8">第一课时：<br><br><br>第二课时：<br><br></td></tr>
<tr>
