<div class="hdwiki_tmml">第一次课程提纲</div>
<table class="table" align="left" width="100%">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>上课准备提纲</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>志愿者信息</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>备课人</strong><br></td>
<td>BLUEBLOOD</td>
<td><strong>Email/MSN</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="3"><br></td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>所属课程组</strong><br></td>
<td>音乐组</td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>课程信息</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>课程名称</strong><br></td>
<td>音乐课</td>
<td><strong>上课日期</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">2012.3.17</td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>上课时长</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">100分钟</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课对象</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">经纬学校3~5年级学生</td>
<td><strong>学生信息</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="5">19人</td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="3"><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ）</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="6"><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N）</strong></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课目标<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8">乐理知识:了解音,五线谱等知识<br><br>动手互助: 互助完成向日葵折纸</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课内容</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8">乐理知识:<br>1 什么是音?<br>2 音的性质有哪些？<br>3 对钢琴和钢琴键盘的基本认识<br>4 音级对应的名称：音名和唱名<br>5 五线谱的谱面构成<br>6 音符的结构<br><br>-<a class="innerlink" title="音乐教案链接" href="index.php?doc-innerlink-%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E6%95%99%E6%A1%88%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5">音乐教案链接</a>: http://www.ygclub.org/wiki/index.php?doc-view-719.html<br>-折纸教程链接: http://www.tudou.com/programs/view/BDUopdON3Ic/<br><br>动手互助: 向日葵折纸</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课提纲<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8">一、自我介绍(0'~15')<br>
1 老师介绍 小节目表演<br>2 学生介绍&nbsp;<br>3 分组<br><br>
二、乐理知识学习(20'~50')<br><br>1&nbsp;什么是音?<br>
2&nbsp;音的性质有哪些？<br>
3&nbsp;对钢琴和钢琴键盘的基本认识<br>
4&nbsp;音级对应的名称：音名和唱名<br><br>
<br>
三、课间休息<br><br>
<br>
四、乐理知识学习(50'~70')<br><br>5&nbsp;五线谱的谱面构成<br>
6&nbsp;音符的结构<br>
<br>五 &nbsp;动手互助:(70'~90')<br><br>&nbsp; 由主讲教大家向日葵折纸,由助教协助各组的学生完成<br>
<br>
六、总结/回顾(90'~100')<br><br>七 其他</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>教学环境、材料需求</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8">教室:有桌椅的教室<br>钢琴:需要大家搬动<br>学生随堂学习手册:<br>折纸材料:主讲准备<br><br><br><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>助教需求<br></strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br>1 助教职责与额外要求<br>2 助教/旁听需准备一个简短的自我介绍和小节目<br>3 协助分组与互动 记录本组学生的上课状态以及表现,为填写随堂手册做准备!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<br>4 前提看一下折纸教程,协助主讲教授折纸.<br>5 提前熟悉音乐课教案,知道如何引导,知道本组学生.<br><br><br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table>
<p><br></p>
