<TD colSpan=3><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2><strong>所属课程组</strong><BR></TD>
<TD><BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=9>
<P align=center><strong>课程信息</strong></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>课程名称</strong><BR></TD>
<TD>U1&amp;U2<BR></TD>
<TD><strong>上课日期</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2>10.13<BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2><strong>上课时长</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2><BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课对象</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=2>四年级<BR></TD>
<TD><strong>学生信息</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=5><BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD colSpan=3>
<P><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（）Y</strong></P></TD>
<TD colSpan=6><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（）Y </strong></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课目标<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8><BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课内容</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P>S1.&nbsp;Review:<BR>1. 数字1-10:&nbsp;<BR>1) 报数<BR>2) 听写<BR>2. 接龙:&nbsp;What’s&nbsp;in&nbsp;our&nbsp;classroom?&nbsp;I/We&nbsp;have&nbsp;a&nbsp;&nbsp;_____./&nbsp;数词&nbsp;_____s.（不能重复）<BR>3. 热身：<BR>1) 老师说词组，学生做动作：open&nbsp;the&nbsp;door&nbsp;/&nbsp;clean&nbsp;the&nbsp;window/&nbsp;put&nbsp;up&nbsp;a&nbsp;picture&nbsp;<BR>2) 老师做动作，学生说词组：clean&nbsp;the&nbsp;board/&nbsp;sweep&nbsp;the&nbsp;floor/&nbsp;turn&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;light<BR><BR>S2.&nbsp;Jessie&nbsp;负责：New&nbsp;words:&nbsp;pen,&nbsp;pencil,&nbsp;ruler,&nbsp;pencil-case,&nbsp;eraser,&nbsp;sharpener,&nbsp;cryon,&nbsp;math&nbsp;book,&nbsp;English&nbsp;book,&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;book,&nbsp;notebook,&nbsp;story&nbsp;book,&nbsp;picture&nbsp;book,&nbsp;schoolbag&nbsp;&nbsp;<BR><BR>S3.&nbsp;Jessie负责：&nbsp;New&nbsp;sentence&nbsp;patterns:<BR>What's&nbsp;in&nbsp;your&nbsp;schoolbag?&nbsp;I&nbsp;have&nbsp;a&nbsp;______.&nbsp;What&nbsp;colour&nbsp;is&nbsp;it？It's&nbsp;________.（对话a)<BR>What's&nbsp;in&nbsp;your&nbsp;schoolbag?&nbsp;I&nbsp;have&nbsp;___________(复数）What&nbsp;colour&nbsp;are&nbsp;they?&nbsp;They&nbsp;are__________.(对话b)<BR><BR>S4.&nbsp;Test:&nbsp;What’s&nbsp;this/that?&nbsp;It’s&nbsp;a/an&nbsp;________.&nbsp;<BR>1. 随便抽学生问（上单元单词），答对的在其书上盖笑脸章<BR>2. 主讲将所有物品放于书包中，问学生What’s&nbsp;in&nbsp;my&nbsp;bag?&nbsp;找学生从中拿出一件物品后回答(It’s&nbsp;a/an&nbsp;_____或者They’re&nbsp;数词+_____s)，答对的暂时保管该物品<BR>3. 总结：What&nbsp;的意思？&nbsp;This/that&nbsp;的意思？It’s=It&nbsp;is/&nbsp;a、an&nbsp;、they’re=they&nbsp;are<BR><BR>S5.&nbsp;New&nbsp;numbers:<BR>1. 11-20带读并纠正发音<BR>2. 数字卡片游戏：<BR>1) 老师说数字，学生在纸上写出来并大声念出来。<BR>2) 老师举数字卡片，学生抢答。</P>
<P>S6.&nbsp;Survey:<BR>&nbsp;How&nbsp;many&nbsp;________do&nbsp;you&nbsp;have?&nbsp;I&nbsp;have___________.<BR><BR>学生在全班范围内做调查，看谁在规定时间内问得最多，选调查中数量最多的物品展示：&nbsp;XX&nbsp;has&nbsp;______________.<BR><BR>S7.字母<BR>1. A-G书写（大小写）<BR>2. 发音规则，练习拼读：ant;&nbsp;cat;&nbsp;boy;&nbsp;car,&nbsp;desk;&nbsp;bed;&nbsp;elephant;&nbsp;Farm;&nbsp;good;&nbsp;goose<BR></P></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课提纲<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8><BR></TD></TR>
