<td><strong>授课目标<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课内容</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8">一、抽签分组（3组13人）<br>
<br>
二、热身<br>
教英文歌《Ali&nbsp;Baba's&nbsp;farm》第一段<br>
http://www.en8848.com.cn/Children/songs/animals/150841.html<br>
助教可以先学学，蛮容易的。<br>
<br>
三、新句型学习。<br>
1、讲方位（on…/in…）<br>
2、复习接下来句型需要的单词(图片)<br>
phone,&nbsp;ice&nbsp;cream,&nbsp;key,&nbsp;bed,&nbsp;toothbrush<br>
table,&nbsp;fridge,&nbsp;sofa,&nbsp;bedroom,&nbsp;bathroom<br>
2、句型<br>
Where&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;…?&nbsp;(&nbsp;phone,&nbsp;ice&nbsp;cream,&nbsp;key,&nbsp;bed,&nbsp;toothbrush)<br>
It&nbsp;is&nbsp;…&nbsp;(on&nbsp;the&nbsp;table,&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;fridge,&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;sofa,&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;bedroom,&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;bathroom)<br>
3、游戏<br>
把图片分别发到每个学生手上。<br>
老师只黑板上的词（phone,&nbsp;ice&nbsp;cream,&nbsp;key,&nbsp;bed,&nbsp;toothbrush）<br>
拿到对应词的学生站起来问句子。<br>
拿到on&nbsp;the&nbsp;table,&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;fridge,&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;sofa,&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;bedroom,&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;bathroom的学生站起来回答句子。<br>
每个人反应的时间为10秒，看哪个组反应最快。<br>
<br>
四、新单词学习。<br>
1、In&nbsp;the&nbsp;kitchen(环境)<br>
单词：Knife,&nbsp;spoon,&nbsp;plate,&nbsp;fork,&nbsp;chopsticks<br>
2、记单词游戏<br>
每组派出代表抽图片，表演图片上的物品让其他学生猜<br>
3、小组练习<br>
Can&nbsp;I&nbsp;help&nbsp;you?(分情景：切菜，喝汤，装菜、吃水果、夹菜的时候。)<br>
Pass&nbsp;me&nbsp;a&nbsp;…,&nbsp;please.<br>
<br>
<br>
五、英文歌《Ali&nbsp;Baba's&nbsp;farm》<br>
整首学习，表演。</td></tr>
