<td colspan="3">lxv1207@163.com</td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>所属课程组</strong><br></td>
<td>英语组</td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>课程信息</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>课程名称</strong><br></td>
<td>六年级英语</td>
<td><strong>上课日期</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">2012年9月22日</td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>上课时长</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课对象</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">六年级学生</td>
<td><strong>学生信息</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="5"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="3">
<p><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（）</strong></p></td>
<td colspan="6"><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（）</strong></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课目标<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8">
<p style=""><b>U1---U2 &nbsp;&nbsp;</b></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课内容</strong></td><td colspan="8"><p style=""><b>S1&nbsp;Review</b><br>
将学生分为三组，助教老师坐到学生中间<br>
解决上节课遗留问题:<br>
Ambulance&nbsp;['æmbjʊl(ə)ns]救护车<br>
钓鱼岛Diaoyu&nbsp;Island&nbsp;/&nbsp;fishing&nbsp;island<br>
Hospital医院<br>
Helicopter直升机<br>
Time&nbsp;machine时光机<br>
Space&nbsp;ship太空飞船<br>
Mars火星<br>
Moon月球<br>
Earth地球<br>
检查homework&nbsp;（用第三人称单数介绍家人工作，上学，外出的出行方式）<br>
复习句型(主讲领读，学生跟读)<br>
How&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;go&nbsp;to&nbsp;school?-I&nbsp;go&nbsp;to&nbsp;school&nbsp;by&nbsp;bus.<br>
How&nbsp;dose&nbsp;she/he&nbsp;go&nbsp;to&nbsp;school?-She/he&nbsp;goes&nbsp;to&nbsp;school&nbsp;by&nbsp;bike.<br>
副词always，usually，often，sometimes，never加入句型<br>
<br><b>
S2&nbsp;Presentation</b><br>
Team&nbsp;work<br>
四人一组练习句型,&nbsp;换成不同的地点，使用适当的交通工具完成下表，然后派一位代表介绍本组情况。（助教可帮忙统计表格，然后每个人在组内需要介绍其他几人的出行方式，最后组内决定选一位代表来完成本组的介绍，包括自己）<br>
<br>
-How&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;go&nbsp;to&nbsp;school/work/Shanghai/US/moon?<br>
-I&nbsp;always/usually/often/sometimes/never&nbsp;go&nbsp;to&nbsp;school&nbsp;by&nbsp;walk。<br>
I&nbsp;usually&nbsp;go&nbsp;to&nbsp;school&nbsp;by&nbsp;walk。&nbsp;Li&nbsp;Qing&nbsp;often&nbsp;goes&nbsp;to&nbsp;school&nbsp;by&nbsp;bike…..<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;By&nbsp;bike&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;By&nbsp;bus&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Walk&nbsp;to&nbsp;school&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;By&nbsp;car<br>
Li&nbsp;Qing&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;√&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
…&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
（拓展部分：解释乘坐该交通工具的原因My&nbsp;home&nbsp;is&nbsp;near/it’s&nbsp;expensive/cheap/faraway/convenient/fast）<br>
<br><b>
S3&nbsp;Traffic&nbsp;lights&nbsp;and&nbsp;rules</b><br>
Stop&nbsp;at&nbsp;a&nbsp;red&nbsp;light<br>
Wait&nbsp;at&nbsp;a&nbsp;yellow&nbsp;light<br>
Go&nbsp;at&nbsp;a&nbsp;green&nbsp;light<br>
Turn&nbsp;right/left/&nbsp;go&nbsp;straight<br>
No&nbsp;right/left&nbsp;turn/bike<br>
<br>
方位词：On&nbsp;the&nbsp;right,&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;left,&nbsp;in&nbsp;front,&nbsp;behind,&nbsp;near,&nbsp;far<br>
认识方位的小游戏：全班起立，主讲发口令：Turn&nbsp;right/left/around<br>
然后学生发口令，可以要求任何一位同学或者助教配合。（计分，&nbsp;如果出错，回答者组需要被扣分，发口令者组得分，不出错折双方都得分，每回合先发口令5次）<br>
<br>
学生分组，组内介绍自己前后左右分别坐的是谁，助教老师帮忙检查：<br>
I’m&nbsp;Karen,&nbsp;lily&nbsp;is&nbsp;on&nbsp;my&nbsp;left,&nbsp;cicy&nbsp;is&nbsp;on&nbsp;my&nbsp;right,&nbsp;&nbsp;jack&nbsp;is&nbsp;in&nbsp;front&nbsp;of&nbsp;me,&nbsp;bill&nbsp;seat&nbsp;behind&nbsp;of&nbsp;me.<br>
<br><b>
S4&nbsp;Vocabulary</b><br>
Hospital,&nbsp;if&nbsp;you&nbsp;are&nbsp;sick/ill,&nbsp;where&nbsp;should&nbsp;you&nbsp;go?<br>
Cinema,&nbsp;if&nbsp;you&nbsp;want&nbsp;to&nbsp;see&nbsp;a&nbsp;movie,&nbsp;where&nbsp;should&nbsp;you&nbsp;go?<br>
Post&nbsp;office,&nbsp;if&nbsp;you&nbsp;want&nbsp;to&nbsp;send&nbsp;a&nbsp;letter,&nbsp;where&nbsp;should&nbsp;you&nbsp;go?<br>
Bookstore,&nbsp;if&nbsp;you&nbsp;want&nbsp;to&nbsp;buy&nbsp;a&nbsp;book&nbsp;where&nbsp;should&nbsp;you&nbsp;go?<br>
Science&nbsp;museum,&nbsp;shopping&nbsp;center,&nbsp;zoo,&nbsp;bank,&nbsp;super&nbsp;market&nbsp;<br>
<br>
Sentence<br>
Where&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;bank?<br>
It’s&nbsp;near&nbsp;the&nbsp;supermarket.<br>
There&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;library&nbsp;in&nbsp;front&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;shopping&nbsp;center.<br>
Where&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;trash&nbsp;bin?<br>
It’s&nbsp;near&nbsp;the&nbsp;table.<br>
Where&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;picture?<br>
It’s&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;wall.<br>
Where&nbsp;is&nbsp;your&nbsp;book?<br>
It’s&nbsp;on&nbsp;my&nbsp;desk.<br>
<br><b>
S5&nbsp;homework</b><br>
每个人画一幅画，自己的居住环境，途中至少要包含5处生活中常去的场所，用英文标注，然后用所学英文介绍，不少于3句话。</p></td></tr>
<tr>
