<td><strong>授课目标<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课内容</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8"><br>
Unit&nbsp;3&nbsp;What&nbsp;are&nbsp;you&nbsp;going&nbsp;to&nbsp;do-&nbsp;Part&nbsp;2<br>
<br>
9:30-9:40<br>
<br>
-&nbsp;点名，介绍主讲，重申课堂小规则。&nbsp;3min<br>
<br>
-&nbsp;提出组长轮换，上届组长辅助。选出新组长。5min<br>
<br>
-&nbsp;学习方法介绍：英文是工具，比起看，更要注重听和说。多说多背，真的遇到外国人或者要张口说英文的时候才不会发怵。提倡听背。2min<br>
9:45-9:55<br>
单词游戏:&nbsp;Hangman&nbsp;Game<br>
(10分/&nbsp;单词+1,&nbsp;意思+1)<br>
复习上节课单词<br>
:&nbsp;Afternoon,<br>
cinema,&nbsp;morning,&nbsp;bookstore,&nbsp;evening<br>
（助教老师，注意这段不能帮孩子猜测可能的单词。只能告诉他们我给的clue是什么意思。）<br>
<br>
9:55&nbsp;–&nbsp;10:20<br>
Unit&nbsp;3&nbsp;词汇&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;句型<br>
单词：Magazine,<br>
Dictionary,&nbsp;Comic&nbsp;Book&nbsp;(comics),&nbsp;newspaper&nbsp;(news),<br>
句型：&nbsp;Where/&nbsp;When/&nbsp;Who<br>
<br>
Where&nbsp;are&nbsp;going&nbsp;to&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;afternoon?<br>
<br>
-&nbsp;I’m&nbsp;going&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;Cinema/&nbsp;book&nbsp;store/&nbsp;shopping&nbsp;mall/&nbsp;school/&nbsp;the&nbsp;Mars<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
When&nbsp;are&nbsp;you&nbsp;going/&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;xxx?<br>
<br>
-&nbsp;I’m&nbsp;going&nbsp;to&nbsp;there&nbsp;at&nbsp;3&nbsp;o’clock/&nbsp;this&nbsp;weekend/&nbsp;next&nbsp;monthly/&nbsp;after&nbsp;20&nbsp;years.<br>
<br>
Who&nbsp;is&nbsp;this?<br>
<br>
-&nbsp;This&nbsp;is&nbsp;xxx.<br>
上节课句型：What&nbsp;are&nbsp;you&nbsp;going&nbsp;to&nbsp;buy&nbsp;(this&nbsp;afternonn/x/x/x)?<br>
<br>
-&nbsp;I’m&nbsp;going&nbsp;to&nbsp;buy&nbsp;xxx/&nbsp;do&nbsp;something<br>
词组：&nbsp;go&nbsp;to&nbsp;cinema/&nbsp;shoping&nbsp;mall/&nbsp;forbidden&nbsp;city/&nbsp;summer&nbsp;palace/<br>
<br>
take&nbsp;a&nbsp;trip<br>
<br>
<br>
plant&nbsp;trees<br>
<br>
visit&nbsp;someone&nbsp;/&nbsp;Say&nbsp;hi<br>
<br>
Read&nbsp;a&nbsp;magazine/&nbsp;newspaper/&nbsp;comic&nbsp;books<br>
<br>
10:20-10:40&nbsp;Break<br>
10:40-10:50<br>
助教协助示范课堂表演<br>
（地点：书店/&nbsp;道具：书，桌子/&nbsp;A&nbsp;是小店主，Chelly和B是店主的朋友，&nbsp;C是不耐烦的客户，重要的抖包袱人士)<br>
B:&nbsp;Where&nbsp;are&nbsp;we&nbsp;going&nbsp;right&nbsp;now?<br>
Chelly:&nbsp;The&nbsp;bookstore.&nbsp;I’m&nbsp;going&nbsp;to&nbsp;say&nbsp;hi&nbsp;my&nbsp;best&nbsp;friend.<br>
(A&nbsp;要背对我)<br>
Chelly:&nbsp;Hey,&nbsp;Beauty/&nbsp;Dude!<br>
A:&nbsp;Hey&nbsp;Chelly!&nbsp;What&nbsp;are&nbsp;you&nbsp;doing&nbsp;here?<br>
Chelly:&nbsp;Come&nbsp;on!&nbsp;Of&nbsp;course&nbsp;I’m&nbsp;coming&nbsp;to&nbsp;buy&nbsp;books!<br>
A:&nbsp;Sorry,&nbsp;cause&nbsp;I&nbsp;never&nbsp;see&nbsp;you&nbsp;reading&nbsp;any&nbsp;book.<br>
Chelly:&nbsp;Bullshit!<br>
（C排在chelly和B后面，&nbsp;扮做要付款的客户，抱着书，表现出非常不耐烦的样子，跺脚，看表，翻白眼)<br>
A:&nbsp;Who&nbsp;is&nbsp;this?&nbsp;Your&nbsp;new&nbsp;friend?<br>
Chelly:&nbsp;Yes,&nbsp;this&nbsp;is&nbsp;B.&nbsp;B,&nbsp;this&nbsp;is&nbsp;my&nbsp;best&nbsp;friend&nbsp;A.<br>
B:<br>
Nice&nbsp;to&nbsp;meet&nbsp;you,&nbsp;A!<br>
（C冲上前，把书pang&nbsp;地敲到桌上）<br>
C:&nbsp;I&nbsp;can’t&nbsp;stand&nbsp;anymore!!&nbsp;Take&nbsp;the&nbsp;money,&nbsp;let&nbsp;me&nbsp;goooooo!!<br>
A/&nbsp;B/&nbsp;Chelly:&nbsp;Woooooh&nbsp;(吃惊状).<br>
A:&nbsp;Fine&nbsp;fine&nbsp;(take&nbsp;the&nbsp;money).<br>
(C冲出去)<br>
A&nbsp;(to&nbsp;B&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Chelly):&nbsp;Nice&nbsp;to&nbsp;meet&nbsp;you&nbsp;too,&nbsp;B.&nbsp;Let’s&nbsp;have&nbsp;dinner&nbsp;together&nbsp;sometime!<br>
Chelly&nbsp;:&nbsp;Great!&nbsp;When&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;have&nbsp;time?<br>
C:&nbsp;Tomorrow.<br>
Chelly&nbsp;:&nbsp;Deal!&nbsp;See&nbsp;you&nbsp;tomorrow!<br>
大致给孩子们解释一下上面的意思<br>
告知孩子评分规则<br>
－&nbsp;用上今天的句型+5<br>
－&nbsp;用了上节课的句型+&nbsp;5<br>
－&nbsp;所有同学都表演了+5<br>
－&nbsp;能回答出和别组表演有关的问题<br>
问题&nbsp;a)有没有这节课教的句型，说的什么？+2<br>
<br>
b)&nbsp;有没有上节课句型，说的什么？+2<br>
<br>
c)&nbsp;Who&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;funniest&nbsp;person&nbsp;?&nbsp;+1<br>
<br>
10:50-11:20<br>
各助教老师负责各组的表演准备<br>
－&nbsp;带读单词，确认每个孩子都开口&nbsp;5min<br>
－&nbsp;带读句型，确认每个孩子都开口&nbsp;5&nbsp;min<br>
－&nbsp;帮助设计环节&nbsp;15&nbsp;min<br>
11:20-11:30<br>
各组表演(请助教老师注意提示忘词的孩子)<br>
每组表演2分钟，提问2分钟</td></tr>
