<td><strong>课程名称</strong><br></td>
<td><br></td>
<td><strong>上课日期</strong></td>
<td colspan="2">11.17</td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>上课时长</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课对象</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2"><br></td>
<td><strong>学生信息</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="5"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="3">
<p><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（）</strong></p></td>
<td colspan="6"><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（） </strong></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课目标<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课内容</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8"><br>
9:20-9:30<br>
<br>
-<br>
<br>
点名<br>
-<br>
重选小组长，介绍组长的意义，不以考分论英雄<br>
-<br>
摆桌，四张桌子拼成一个岛，围岛而坐，助教，旁听坐附近<br>
9:30-9:45<br>
-<br>
单词小游戏：拼单词对抗赛<br>
（在前三个单元里的课后单词表里挑选）<br>
A组<br>
中文&nbsp;B组英文<br>
B组中文&nbsp;C组英文<br>
C组中文A组英文<br>
-<br>
介绍本次课堂内容－复习前三单元<br>
带读单词及句型<br>
课堂表演<br>
（规则：每组同学认领一个单元，一起编一个小表演－&gt;编完了后选举出一个人做导演，整理对话－&gt;导演要去教别组怎么演，哪组抽签决定）<br>
9:45&nbsp;–&nbsp;10:05<br>
Unit&nbsp;1&nbsp;How&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;go&nbsp;to&nbsp;school?<br>
-<br>
How&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;go&nbsp;to&nbsp;school/&nbsp;Cinema/&nbsp;Library/&nbsp;Science&nbsp;Museum/&nbsp;the&nbsp;book&nbsp;store/Shopping&nbsp;mall&nbsp;/&nbsp;the&nbsp;moon/&nbsp;Hawaii?<br>
I&nbsp;always/&nbsp;often/&nbsp;usually/&nbsp;go&nbsp;toxxx&nbsp;by&nbsp;walk/&nbsp;bus/&nbsp;taxi/&nbsp;car/&nbsp;train/&nbsp;plane<br>
-<br>
How&nbsp;can&nbsp;I&nbsp;get&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;Park?<br>
You&nbsp;can&nbsp;go&nbsp;by&nbsp;No.409&nbsp;bus,&nbsp;get&nbsp;off&nbsp;at&nbsp;xx&nbsp;station.<br>
Go&nbsp;straight,&nbsp;turn&nbsp;left&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;second&nbsp;traffic&nbsp;light.<br>
Unit&nbsp;2&nbsp;Where&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;Science&nbsp;Musuem?<br>
-<br>
Where&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;science&nbsp;museum?<br>
It&nbsp;is&nbsp;next&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;school,&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;right&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;cinema<br>
Maybe&nbsp;that&nbsp;way,&nbsp;I’m&nbsp;not&nbsp;sure<br>
-<br>
Is&nbsp;it&nbsp;far&nbsp;from&nbsp;here?<br>
No,&nbsp;it&nbsp;is&nbsp;very&nbsp;close.&nbsp;Takes&nbsp;about&nbsp;10&nbsp;minutes&nbsp;to&nbsp;walk.<br>
Unit&nbsp;3&nbsp;What&nbsp;are&nbsp;you&nbsp;going&nbsp;to&nbsp;do?<br>
-<br>
What&nbsp;are&nbsp;you&nbsp;going&nbsp;to&nbsp;do&nbsp;this&nbsp;weekend/&nbsp;Saturday/&nbsp;next&nbsp;year/&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;future?<br>
We&nbsp;are&nbsp;going&nbsp;to&nbsp;have&nbsp;a&nbsp;party&nbsp;on&nbsp;Sunday/<br>
-<br>
When&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;want&nbsp;to&nbsp;start&nbsp;the&nbsp;party?<br>
How&nbsp;about&nbsp;6PM.<br>
-<br>
Who&nbsp;is&nbsp;she?<br>
My&nbsp;best&nbsp;friend<br>
10:05-10:20<br>
各个小组认领单元，编排小话剧。<br>
各组选出小导演，导演无需参演，但要记下所有同学表演的句子和内容，可以调配每个同学演什么。<br>
下课时把剧本交上来。<br>
助教老师是副导演。请带读单词和句型，如果孩子们在编排时如果遇到困难，也请协助。尽量保证孩子们念出来的英文字正腔圆一些。<br>
规则：－<br>
有认领单元句型+5分<br>
<br>
－<br>
有非认领单元句型+5<br>
Break<br>
10:40-10:45<br>
各组小导演互换，抽签决定。<br>
小导演带上副导演（助教），去新的团队。带领新团队熟悉台词。<br>
助教请协助小导演安排好各个角色。<br>
10:45-11:15&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
<br>
个小组排练时间<br>
11:15-11:30<br>
各组表演<br>
每组表演3分钟，提问2分钟<br>
<br>
规则<br>
<br>
－&nbsp;所有同学参演+5<br>
-&nbsp;回答出问题+5</td></tr>
