<div class="hdwiki_tmml">第五次活动</div>
<BR>上课准备提纲 <BR><BR>志愿者信息 <BR><BR>备课人: Apple<BR>Email/MSN&nbsp;<BR><A href="mailto:lijia2367@gmail.com">lijia2367@gmail.com</A><BR>所属课程组 <BR>English <BR><BR>课程信息 <BR><BR>课程名称: English <BR><BR>上课日期 <BR>April 17th, 2010 <BR>上课时长 <BR>100分钟 <BR><BR>授课对象&nbsp;<BR>初一 <BR>学生信息 <BR>12 students <BR><BR>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ） <BR>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（Y） <BR>授课目标 <BR>科学概念： <BR>过程与方法： <BR>情感、态度、价值观： <BR><BR>授课内容 <BR>Main tasks: <BR>- Review of "what they have learnt" <BR>- Review of "Is this your shirt?" <BR>- Learn to write an English poem <BR><BR><BR>授课提纲 <BR>第一课时： <BR>What is your English name?（10mins) <BR>- Q by teacher and A by students <BR><BR>Review of "words and expressions" (10 mins) <BR>- Emphasize the difficult parts like the second line <BR><BR>Sentences review and pair practice：(10 mins) <BR>- Is this your skirt? <BR>- Yes, it is. <BR>- No, it isn't. <BR>- Are those your pants? <BR>- Yes, they are. <BR>- I like my blue sweater. <BR>- My yellow shirt is too small. <BR><BR>Game: What do you want to wear today? (10mins) <BR>- show the pictures of wears <BR>- select students to choose their favourite wears <BR><BR>Poem appreciation <BR>5.1 Meaning of the poem: (10 mins) <BR>Seasons <BR>Spring is green， <BR>Summer is bright， <BR>Autumn is gold， <BR>Winter is white. <BR>Year in year out， <BR>We work and fight， <BR>For a new world， <BR>of red sunlight <BR><BR>第二课时： <BR><BR>5.2 Try to read the poem: (10 mins) <BR><BR>Structure of an English poem: (10 mins) <BR>Spring, Spring, Spring, <BR>Lovely Spring, <BR>Sweet Spring. <BR>Spring is beautiful, <BR>Spring is bird's singing. <BR>Oh, I love you, my Spring. <BR><BR>Write an English poem（20 mins) <BR><BR>Selected students to read their poems ：(10 mins) <BR>教学环境、材料需求 :彩笔，白纸，彩图<BR>助教需求 <BR><BR>YES <BR><BR><BR>
<div class="hdwiki_tmml">第六次活动</div>
<P>cinderella剧本节选链接：<BR><A href="http://www.ygclub.org/wiki/index.php?doc-view-309.html">http://www.ygclub.org/wiki/index.php?doc-view-309.html</A></P>
<P>2010年4月24日平西府课程大纲 <BR>基本信息 <BR>备课人: jeccili <BR>Email/MSN: jeccili@hotmail.com <BR>课程名称: English <BR>上课日: April 24th, 2010 <BR>上课时长: 100min <BR>授课对象: 初一 <BR>学生人数：12 <BR>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y） <BR>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N） <BR><BR>授课信息 <BR>I. 教学重点： <BR>- 复习英文自然拼读法 <BR>- 解答(emily)动名词变化规律 <BR>- 排演Cinderella剧本 <BR>II. Preparations <BR>1. Cinderella剧本打印（25张） <BR>2. 学会简单舞步（以便教小朋友们完成剧本里dance部分） <BR>3. 道具准备：大臣、王子、灰姑娘标牌（有小皇冠和后冠更好） <BR>4. 做签：大臣1、大臣2、灰姑娘、王子各两张 <BR>III. Contents <BR>【first class】 <BR>1. greetings; self-introduction（3’） <BR>2. speaking practice(10’) <BR>a. how are you today? <BR>b. Using the phrase ‘I miss you much.’(which Apple taught us three weeks before in ‘big big world’) <BR>3. 介绍今天课程内容(3’) <BR>4. review the phonics rule（10’） <BR>a. read the following words: chimpanzee黑猩猩; Hippopotamus河马; Crocodile 鳄鱼; Squirrel 松鼠; Peacock 孔雀; <BR>b. give a concise conclusion：结尾有字母e 间隔有元音的单词发音规律 <BR>c. read the following words: minister, prince, Cinderella, highness(guess what are we going to learn today?) <BR>5. 解答动名词变化规律（10’） <BR>a. 一般情况/以不发音的字母e结尾/以字母ie结尾/重读闭音节结尾 <BR>6. 分发剧本[助教帮忙](2’) <BR>7. act it out with assistants exaggeratedly(12’) <BR>【second class】 <BR>1. 剧本内容梳理（15’） <BR>主要包括： <BR>a. 词汇解释; 整句句子解释;纠正发音 <BR>b. showing how to act with the help of assistants <BR>c. direct acting practice with students <BR>2. divide eight girls into two groups(如果人多再加助教组建一组;人少助教顶替); <BR>3. acting practice[助教帮忙;其他志愿者参与视情况而定]（15’） <BR>4. presentation(20’) <BR>notion: <BR>a. teach how to dance; <BR>b. the audience act as ‘soldiers’ and shout out aloud in performances; <BR>c. 鼓励夸张 <BR><BR>the end. <BR><BR><BR><BR><BR>【attachments】 <BR>I. <BR>1. Phonics Rule No. 1 :long vowels <BR>a) a as in ape, ate, cake, late, make <BR>b) ee as in green, tree, sweet, sleep <BR>c) i as in bite, light, kind, white, rice <BR>d) o as in hole, ghost, fold, no, pole <BR>e) u as in lunar, June, lute, flu <BR>f) y as in shy, fly, sly <BR>2. Phonics Rule No. 2 : short vowels <BR>a) a as in apple, mat, bad, land, fat <BR>b) e as in red, net, pet, wet, bed <BR>c) i as in bit, dictionary, ship, king, in <BR>d) o as in fog, frog, hot, lot, pot <BR>e) u as in uncle, bus, must, mud, cut <BR>f) y as in lily, silly, beauty, ready, belly <BR>3. Rule No. 3: vowel combination <BR>“when two vowels go walking, the first one does the talking”. <BR>ai/ay as in day, say, play, spray, and tray <BR>ea as in eat, sea, each, leaf, peach, mean, team, ease <BR>oa as in oat, boat, coat, groan <BR>ue as in blue, glue, clue, true <BR>ui as in suit, fruit, juice <BR>4. Phonics Rule No. 4 silent “gh”（10’） <BR>augh, eigh, igh <BR>a) Listen and select the words <BR>ambulence,absolutely, backwards, beanstalk, confident, cafeteria, darkness, dashboard, fabulous, featherweight, internet, helicopter, impossible, intelligence, judgement, kangaroo, liberty, library, magazine, mysterious, necessary, nickname, package, pocketbook, raccoon, ridiculous, satisfaction, secondary, secretary, touchstone, timetable, victory, vaccine, wonderland, woodpecker, xylophone, yogurt, yesterday, zigzag <BR><BR>II. <BR>动词现在分词由动词原形在词尾加ing构成，其规则如下： <BR>1.一般情况下直接加ingthink---thinking <BR>sleep---sleeping <BR>study---studying <BR>speak---speaking <BR>say---saying <BR>carry---carrying <BR>2.以不发音的字母e结尾的单词，去掉字母e，再加ingwake---waking <BR>make---making <BR>come---coming <BR>take---taking <BR>leave---leaving <BR>have---having <BR>3.以ie结尾的动词，把ie改为y ，再加ing die---dying <BR>lie---lying <BR>4.以重读闭音节结尾，呈现“辅，元，辅”结构的动词，先双写末尾的辅音字母，再加ing <BR>stop---stopping <BR>sit---sitting <BR>run---running <BR>forget---forgetting <BR>begin---beginning <BR>e.g. begin，cut, get, hit, run, set, sit, spit, stop, swim, beg, drop, fit, nod, dig, forget, regret, rid, etc. <BR><BR></P>
<div class="hdwiki_tmml">第七次活动</div>
<strong>教学目标：</strong> <BR>1. 复习自然拼读法，A E I O U Y 几个元音字母的基本发音规则（发长元音和短元音的两种情况）以及基本的元音字母组合的发音规则 <BR>2. 复习Cinderella 剧目、自如表演 <BR>3. 关于服装的词汇和日常用语 <BR><strong>详细教案： <BR></strong>【First Class】 <BR>1. warm-up game: quick wit relay (10’） <BR>A toy is passed randomly among all the paticipants. Anyone who gets the toy has to finish a task before she can pass it to the next person. Tasks progresses in two levels. <BR>Level 1: the first person to throw the toy gives an English letter, the next person who gets the toy must instantly give two letters, first of which should be next to the given letter in the alphabet; second of which,on the contrary, should be at least two letters away from the given letter. <BR>Level 2: the first person to throw the toy gives an English word, the next person who gets the toy must instantly give two words, first of which should be related in some way with the given word; second of which,on the contrary, should be utterly irrelevant with the given word. <BR>2. Review the vowels: A E I O U and Y （10’） <BR>group contest – word hunt: find out as many as possible words with long vowels and short vowels <BR>3. Review vowel combinations (25) <BR>introducing Rule No. 3: when two vowels go walking, the first one does the talking. <BR>eg. ai/ay, ea, ie , oa, oe, ou, ue, ui <BR>【Second Class】 <BR>1. Review the lines from Cinderella(10’) <BR>2. Cinderella drama performance (10’) <BR>3. Draw the princess in your imagination(5’) <BR>4. Princess dress from head to toe <BR>a) crown, tiara, ribbon, gold, silver, diamond, peal, precious stone <BR>b) dress, coat, straight skirt, belt, pants, <BR>c) jewelry, earrings, necklace, bracelet, ring <BR>d) boots, high heels, sandles, slippers, sneakers <BR><BR><strong>教学效果和分析：</strong> <BR>第一节课只来了三个学生，而且都是迟到了一刻钟左右才到，自然拼音的知识基本上都已经忘得差不多了，而且不像第一次接触时候那样有兴趣，教学效果很不理想。 <BR>第二节课又来了两个孩子，而且两个人状态都比较积极，这节课的课堂气氛有明显的改善。通过Alphabet Box（即依照字母表的顺序回忆从A-Z开头的与主题相关的单词）的方式来“头脑风暴” Cinderella 故事中涉及的单词，孩子们对这种方式还是比较有兴趣，反馈很积极。最后的表演中，Alice和Cindy的搭档掀了一个小高潮。 <BR>对下次课的建议： <BR>孩子们的词汇积累非常有限，甚至一个基础相对较好的学生，连“hat”都表示没有学过。因此在进行自然拼音的举例之时，孩子们的参与度很差，因为完全想不出什么单词来。第一次上课时因为有助教的帮助效果还不错，这次复习就完全表现出了孩子的真实水平。 <BR>同时，第二节课Alphabet Box的游戏孩子们参与度比较好，反映出以孩子目前的基础，以主题来梳理单词，效果比较好。以后应当有意识地帮助孩子进行这种梳理，选择一些有趣的主题，把相关单词集中起来串讲。 <BR><BR><BR><BR>
