<P>计划了4课时的教学内容，下周的课希望能够做好衔接。</P>
<div class="hdwiki_tmml">第九次活动</div>
上课准备提纲<br>
志愿者信息<br>
备课人  Julia Email/MSN cuiyingshan@yahoo.com.cn  所属课程组  英语<br>
课程信息<br>
课程名称  英语课  上课日期  2010.6.5  上课时长  2小时/50分钟一堂<br>
授课对象  平西府弘立学校五年级学生  学生信息  10人<br>
是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y&nbsp;/&nbsp;N）Y  本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（Y&nbsp;/&nbsp;N）Y<br>
授课目标  1.  完整表演Cinderella小短剧<br>
授课内容  1.  复习短剧重点词汇<br>
2.  复习短剧重点句型<br>
3.  分组排练短剧<br>
授课提纲  第一堂<br>
1.  暖场会话：<br>
• 请学生讲解灰姑娘的故事&nbsp;–&nbsp;介绍并描述其中的人物：&nbsp;<br>
• Cinderella<br>
• Sister<br>
• Stepmother<br>
• Fairy<br>
<br>
2.  引导同学讲解第一、二幕，并分4人一组练习一遍（需要助教配合）<br>
ACT&nbsp;I&nbsp;      AT&nbsp;HOME&nbsp;<br>
Sister&nbsp;A:&nbsp;    Cinderella,&nbsp;clean&nbsp;the&nbsp;kitchen!&nbsp;<br>
Cinderella:&nbsp;   Yes!&nbsp;<br>
Sister&nbsp;B:&nbsp;    Cinderella,&nbsp;cook&nbsp;the&nbsp;meat!&nbsp;<br>
Cinderella:&nbsp;   OK.&nbsp;<br>
Step&nbsp;mother:&nbsp; Cinderella!&nbsp;Cinderella!&nbsp;Wash&nbsp;the&nbsp;clothes!&nbsp;<br>
Cinderella:&nbsp;   I’m&nbsp;coming!&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
<br>
ACT&nbsp;II&nbsp;     THE&nbsp;INVITATION&nbsp;<br>
Sister&nbsp;A:&nbsp;    Look,&nbsp;an&nbsp;invitation&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;king!&nbsp;<br>
Sister&nbsp;B:&nbsp;    We&nbsp;are&nbsp;invited&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;ball&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;Palace！&nbsp;<br>
Step&nbsp;Mother:&nbsp; Cinderella,&nbsp;come&nbsp;help&nbsp;your&nbsp;sisters&nbsp;get&nbsp;dressed!&nbsp;<br>
Cinderella:&nbsp;   OK…can&nbsp;I&nbsp;go&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;ball,&nbsp;too?&nbsp;<br>
Sisters&nbsp;A:&nbsp;   You?&nbsp;Look&nbsp;at&nbsp;you!&nbsp;You&nbsp;don’t&nbsp;even&nbsp;have&nbsp;a&nbsp;dress!&nbsp;<br>
<br>
3.  第三幕单词讲解学习&nbsp;–&nbsp;Fairy，Godmother，garden，pumpkin，coach，&nbsp;&nbsp;mice，&nbsp;horses，&nbsp;&nbsp;footman，dress&nbsp;up，beautiful&nbsp;，remember，midnight<br>
<br>
4.  引导同学讲解第三幕，并分2人一组练习（需要助教配合）<br>
ACT&nbsp;III&nbsp;      THE&nbsp;FAIRY&nbsp;<br>
Fairy:&nbsp;      Don’t&nbsp;cry&nbsp;Cinderella,&nbsp;I’ll&nbsp;help&nbsp;you.&nbsp;<br>
Cinderella:&nbsp;   Who&nbsp;are&nbsp;you?&nbsp;<br>
Fairy:&nbsp;      I’m&nbsp;your&nbsp;Fairy&nbsp;Godmother.&nbsp;Now&nbsp;go&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;garden&nbsp;and&nbsp;find&nbsp;a&nbsp;<br>
nice,&nbsp;big&nbsp;pumpkin.&nbsp;I’ll&nbsp;turn&nbsp;it&nbsp;into&nbsp;your&nbsp;coach.&nbsp;And&nbsp;I’ll&nbsp;turn&nbsp;these&nbsp;mice&nbsp;into&nbsp;horses.&nbsp;And&nbsp;your&nbsp;cat&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;your&nbsp;footman.&nbsp;ABRACADABRA!&nbsp;<br>
Cinderella:&nbsp;   Wow!&nbsp;<br>
Fairy:&nbsp;      Now&nbsp;it’s&nbsp;time&nbsp;to&nbsp;dress&nbsp;up.&nbsp;ABRACADABRA!&nbsp;<br>
Cinderella:&nbsp;   Wow,&nbsp;my&nbsp;dress!&nbsp;<br>
Fairy:&nbsp;      You&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;the&nbsp;most&nbsp;beautiful&nbsp;girl&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;ball.&nbsp;But&nbsp;remember,&nbsp;you&nbsp;<br>
must&nbsp;come&nbsp;back&nbsp;before&nbsp;the&nbsp;midnight.&nbsp;<br>
Cinderella:&nbsp;   Thank&nbsp;you&nbsp;so&nbsp;much,&nbsp;godmother!&nbsp;<br>
<br>
第二堂<br>
5.  引导同学回顾第三幕的故事<br>
6.  第四幕单词讲解学习&nbsp;–Minister，&nbsp;King，Prince&nbsp;，Godmother，queen，&nbsp;garden，son&nbsp;，enter，&nbsp;struck&nbsp;，almost&nbsp;，pretty&nbsp;，princess，house，try&nbsp;on,&nbsp;&nbsp;highness<br>
7.  引导同学讲解第四幕，并分4人一组练习一遍<br>
ACT&nbsp;IX&nbsp;THE&nbsp;BALL<br>
Minister:&nbsp; Ladies&nbsp;and&nbsp;gentlemen,&nbsp;welcome&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;royal&nbsp;ball!&nbsp;Tonight,&nbsp;our&nbsp;prince&nbsp;will&nbsp;select&nbsp;the&nbsp;most&nbsp;beautiful&nbsp;woman&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;his&nbsp;queen.&nbsp;<br>
King:&nbsp;     My&nbsp;son,&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;have&nbsp;anyone&nbsp;in&nbsp;mind?&nbsp;<br>
Prince:&nbsp;     No.&nbsp;I&nbsp;don’t&nbsp;like&nbsp;anyone&nbsp;of&nbsp;them.&nbsp;<br>
Cinderella&nbsp;entered.&nbsp;<br>
Prince:&nbsp;     May&nbsp;I&nbsp;dance&nbsp;with&nbsp;you?&nbsp;<br>
Cinderella:   I’d&nbsp;love&nbsp;to.&nbsp;<br>
<br>
The&nbsp;clock&nbsp;struck.&nbsp;<br>
Cinderella:&nbsp;   Oh,&nbsp;no.&nbsp;It’s&nbsp;almost&nbsp;midnight!&nbsp;Sorry,&nbsp;but&nbsp;I&nbsp;have&nbsp;to&nbsp;leave.&nbsp;<br>
Prince:&nbsp;     Wait!&nbsp;My&nbsp;pretty&nbsp;princess,&nbsp;wait!&nbsp;<br>
Prince:&nbsp;     Take&nbsp;this&nbsp;shoe&nbsp;to&nbsp;every&nbsp;house&nbsp;and&nbsp;let&nbsp;every&nbsp;girl&nbsp;try&nbsp;it&nbsp;on.&nbsp;<br>
Minister:&nbsp;   Yes,&nbsp;your&nbsp;highness.&nbsp;<br>
<br>
8.  第五幕单词讲解学习&nbsp;–short，tight，Of&nbsp;course，perfectly<br>
9.  引导同学讲解第五幕，并分4人一组练习一遍<br>
ACT&nbsp;X&nbsp;THE&nbsp;SHOE&nbsp;<br>
Sister&nbsp;A:&nbsp;    Oh,&nbsp;it’s&nbsp;too&nbsp;short!&nbsp;<br>
Sister&nbsp;B:&nbsp;    No,&nbsp;it’s&nbsp;too&nbsp;tight!&nbsp;<br>
Minister:&nbsp;   Are&nbsp;there&nbsp;any&nbsp;other&nbsp;girls&nbsp;in&nbsp;this&nbsp;house?&nbsp;<br>
Step&nbsp;Mother: No,&nbsp;there&nbsp;aren’t.&nbsp;<br>
Cinderella:&nbsp;   Can&nbsp;I&nbsp;try&nbsp;it&nbsp;on?&nbsp;<br>
Minister:&nbsp;   Of&nbsp;course,&nbsp;please.&nbsp;<br>
Minister:&nbsp;   Ah,&nbsp;it&nbsp;fits&nbsp;perfectly!&nbsp;<br>
10. 争取整剧回顾讲解，分组练习，选取6位同学最终演出<br>

