<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>课程信息</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>课程名称</strong><br></td>
<td>英语</td>
<td><strong>上课日期</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">2011..9.17</td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>上课时长&nbsp;</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">90分钟<br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课对象</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">四年级</td>
<td><strong>学生信息</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="5"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="3"><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ）</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="6"><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N）</strong></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课目标<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8">
<p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课内容</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8">Content Material  Note<br>
Period&nbsp;1&nbsp;&nbsp;Revision&nbsp;In&nbsp;My&nbsp;Classroom<br>
Self-introduction&nbsp;(20&nbsp;minutes)<br>
-&nbsp;My&nbsp;name&nbsp;is&nbsp;Ms./Mr./Miss…<br>
I’m&nbsp;from…&nbsp;<br>
Make&nbsp;your&nbsp;own&nbsp;name&nbsp;tag<br>
Introduce&nbsp;yourself&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;class&nbsp;(五年级的同学可以加上以下两个句式<br>
There&nbsp;are&nbsp;____&nbsp;people&nbsp;in&nbsp;my&nbsp;family:&nbsp;my____,&nbsp;my____,&nbsp;and&nbsp;my_____.&nbsp;My&nbsp;favourite&nbsp;colour/number/animal/weather/season&nbsp;is_________)<br>
<br>
Class&nbsp;rules&nbsp;(15&nbsp;minutes)<br>
尊重(Respect)<br>
尊重他人（Respect&nbsp;Others):&nbsp;老师或同学说话的时候请保持安静。提问或回答问题请安静地举手。小组讨论时请把声音降到最低。<br>
尊重环境：下课时把自己周围收拾干净<br>
<br>
努力（Do&nbsp;my&nbsp;best）<br>
每次上课只需要带三样东西：一只笔，一个本子，家庭作业<br>
做错没有关系，重要的是你试过了<br>
学过的新词尽量马上用<br>
能用英语的时候就用英语<br>
<br>
Seat&nbsp;arrangement<br>
Count&nbsp;from&nbsp;one&nbsp;to&nbsp;five,&nbsp;group&nbsp;students&nbsp;in&nbsp;1s&nbsp;2s&nbsp;3s&nbsp;4s&nbsp;5s<br>
<br>
Questions:<br>
What&nbsp;does&nbsp;it&nbsp;mean?<br>
How&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;spell&nbsp;it?    <br>
<br>
<br>
Vocabulary<br>
Brainstorm:&nbsp;What&nbsp;are&nbsp;there&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;classroom?&nbsp;&nbsp;每个小组在A4纸上写出至少两个单词，把它剪下来，贴到教室里相应的地方<br>
习读单词<br>
游戏：Alphabet&nbsp;Soup&nbsp;<br>
  Blank&nbsp;A4&nbsp;paper,&nbsp;thick&nbsp;colour&nbsp;pens&nbsp;<br>
<br>
sharpener，computer的图（或者让学生自己画） －&nbsp;四、五个人一组，每组用彩笔写出两个词，期待出现的词汇：bag,&nbsp;classroom,&nbsp;boy,&nbsp;girl,&nbsp;desk,&nbsp;pen,&nbsp;pencil,&nbsp;sharpener,&nbsp;window,&nbsp;door,&nbsp;floor,&nbsp;picture,&nbsp;wall,&nbsp;teacher’s&nbsp;desk,&nbsp;computer<br>
－&nbsp;Alphabet&nbsp;Soup:&nbsp;Students&nbsp;have&nbsp;3&nbsp;minutes&nbsp;to&nbsp;find&nbsp;an&nbsp;item&nbsp;within&nbsp;the&nbsp;room&nbsp;&nbsp;that&nbsp;begins&nbsp;with&nbsp;each&nbsp;letter&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;alphabet,&nbsp;in&nbsp;order.&nbsp;They&nbsp;must&nbsp;form&nbsp;a&nbsp;collection&nbsp;on&nbsp;their&nbsp;table&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;items,&nbsp;and&nbsp;cannot&nbsp;reuse&nbsp;an&nbsp;item&nbsp;more&nbsp;than&nbsp;once.&nbsp;At&nbsp;the&nbsp;end&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;time&nbsp;alloted,&nbsp;ask&nbsp;each&nbsp;team&nbsp;how&nbsp;far&nbsp;they&nbsp;got&nbsp;(to&nbsp;which&nbsp;letter),&nbsp;and&nbsp;then&nbsp;go&nbsp;through&nbsp;the&nbsp;alphabet&nbsp;asking&nbsp;each&nbsp;team&nbsp;what&nbsp;they&nbsp;had&nbsp;for&nbsp;each&nbsp;letter&nbsp;and&nbsp;to&nbsp;hold&nbsp;it&nbsp;up.&nbsp;The&nbsp;team&nbsp;that&nbsp;got&nbsp;the&nbsp;furthest,&nbsp;wins!&nbsp;玩这个游戏之前要先复习一下26个字母的排序<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Period&nbsp;2&nbsp;Revision:&nbsp;Is&nbsp;this&nbsp;your&nbsp;skirt?<br>
Warm-up&nbsp;&nbsp;(10&nbsp;minutes)<br>
Find&nbsp;one&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;class&nbsp;room&nbsp;在黑板上写出一个词，让孩子们在教室里找<br>
    可学习一些新词：<br>
eraser,&nbsp;crayon,&nbsp;paper,&nbsp;notebook,&nbsp;ruler,&nbsp;scissors,&nbsp;blackboard,&nbsp;notebook<br>
并重复第一节课的<br>
<br>
Drill&nbsp;(10-15&nbsp;mins)<br>
What&nbsp;is&nbsp;this?&nbsp;<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;What&nbsp;is&nbsp;that?<br>
先老师问，再让学生自己问<br>
This&nbsp;is…<br>
That&nbsp;is…   <br>
Wordsearch&nbsp;(10”)&nbsp;   Worksheet:&nbsp;<br>
classroom&nbsp;word&nbsp;search 链接见文件末<br>
Wrap&nbsp;up&nbsp;and&nbsp;Pairwork:&nbsp;<br>
What’s&nbsp;your&nbsp;name?<br>
What&nbsp;is&nbsp;this/that?<br>
This/That&nbsp;is…<br>
    <br>
http://www.mes-english.com/worksheets/flashcards/classroom_spaghetti.php&nbsp;<br><br></td></tr>
<tr>
