<tr>
<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>课程信息</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>课程名称</strong><br></td>
<td><br></td>
<td><strong>上课日期</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">9月24</td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>上课时长</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">100分钟<br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课对象</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">四年级</td>
<td><strong>学生信息</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="5"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="3"><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ）</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="6"><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N）</strong></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课目标<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8">
<p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课内容</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8"><br>复习2单元</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课提纲<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8">Content Material  Note<br>
Period&nbsp;1&nbsp;&nbsp;Revision&nbsp;In&nbsp;My&nbsp;Classroom<br>
Warm&nbsp;up&nbsp;Revision<br>
抢答游戏：<br>
－&nbsp;准备一些A4纸，在一面印出下列词语的图片：&nbsp;bag,&nbsp;classroom,&nbsp;boy,&nbsp;girl,&nbsp;desk,&nbsp;pen,&nbsp;pencil,&nbsp;sharpener,&nbsp;window,&nbsp;door,&nbsp;floor,&nbsp;picture,&nbsp;wall,&nbsp;teacher’s&nbsp;desk,&nbsp;computer,&nbsp;另一面写上分值（比如50，&nbsp;100，&nbsp;200，&nbsp;400，&nbsp;500等），分值面朝外贴在黑板上<br>
<br>
－&nbsp;每组几张抢答纸，各小组轮流选取分值。所有小组一起限时半分钟写下图片所代表的词<br>
<br>
－&nbsp;在限时内拼写准确的小组可得分<br>
随堂抽答：Free-talk：what’s&nbsp;this?(It’s&nbsp;a&nbsp;pencil.)\\How&nbsp;many&nbsp;pencils&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;have?&nbsp;\\What’s&nbsp;in&nbsp;your&nbsp;pencil-case?）<br>
<br>
&nbsp;<br>
3.&nbsp;Let’s&nbsp;do:&nbsp;Open&nbsp;your&nbsp;pencil-case.&nbsp;Show&nbsp;me&nbsp;your&nbsp;sharpener.&nbsp;Close&nbsp;your&nbsp;book.&nbsp;Carry&nbsp;your&nbsp;bag.&nbsp;Go&nbsp;to&nbsp;school.<br>
<br>
4.&nbsp;出示schoolbag的单词卡片进行教学，并通过跟读与拼读进行操练：&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;book，English&nbsp;book,&nbsp;math&nbsp;book，&nbsp;Story-book,&nbsp;notebook,&nbsp;schoolbag.  教室物品图片：<br>
http://www.esl-kids.com/flashcards/classroom/large-classroom.pdf<br>
<br>
http://www.esl-kids.com/flashcards/classroom/large-classroom2.pdf<br>
  What’s&nbsp;in&nbsp;your&nbsp;…&nbsp;的句型可以巩固扩展一下：<br>
What’s&nbsp;in&nbsp;your&nbsp;schoolbag?&nbsp;What’s&nbsp;in&nbsp;your&nbsp;classroom?&nbsp;What’s&nbsp;in&nbsp;your&nbsp;home?&nbsp;What’s&nbsp;in&nbsp;your&nbsp;desk?&nbsp;让学生两人互相问。<br>
Period&nbsp;2<br>
5.&nbsp;Guessing&nbsp;game:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Teacher&nbsp;shows&nbsp;a&nbsp;schoolbag&nbsp;and&nbsp;asks:What’s&nbsp;in&nbsp;my&nbsp;school?6.&nbsp;&nbsp;Open&nbsp;the&nbsp;schoolbag&nbsp;and&nbsp;show&nbsp;the&nbsp;books,&nbsp;then&nbsp;introduces&nbsp;the&nbsp;books&nbsp;and&nbsp;mast&nbsp;the&nbsp;new&nbsp;words&nbsp;one&nbsp;by&nbsp;one.&nbsp;&nbsp;（边展示各种书本边教学各个英语单词,显得形象具体,使学生在真实的情景中去感知语言）&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Read&nbsp;the&nbsp;words&nbsp;by&nbsp;some&nbsp;ways&nbsp;,then&nbsp;spell&nbsp;and&nbsp;write&nbsp;the&nbsp;words.<br>
  English&nbsp;book&nbsp;<br>
story-book&nbsp;<br>
Chinese&nbsp;book<br>
Notebook<br>
Math&nbsp;book<br>
<br>
<br>
  Heavy<br>
Black&nbsp;white<br>
Purple<br>
Fat<br>
Too&nbsp;many<br>
Twenty-one<br>
Thirty<br>
Forty<br>
fifty<br>
7.Ask&nbsp;and&nbsp;answer:&nbsp;How&nbsp;many&nbsp;books&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;have?&nbsp;I&nbsp;have……&nbsp;.<br>
复习单数、复数<br>
This&nbsp;is…<br>
These&nbsp;are…<br>
That&nbsp;is…<br>
Those&nbsp;are…<br>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;  复数＋s的规则<br>
<br>
8.&nbsp;Pairwork:&nbsp;Ask&nbsp;and&nbsp;answer   <br>
9.&nbsp;Let’s&nbsp;do（1）、Teacher&nbsp;puts&nbsp;the&nbsp;books&nbsp;and&nbsp;asks：Where&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;math&nbsp;book？（2）、Do&nbsp;the&nbsp;actions&nbsp;and&nbsp;mast&nbsp;the&nbsp;words：on、in、under、near..（3）、Listen&nbsp;and&nbsp;do：….（4）、Act&nbsp;like&nbsp;the&nbsp;teacher：<br>
（5）、Listen&nbsp;and&nbsp;do&nbsp;in&nbsp;pairs.    <br>
10.&nbsp;Extra&nbsp;vocabulary&nbsp;<br>
scissors,&nbsp;glue,&nbsp;blackboard,&nbsp;crayon,&nbsp;table http://www.esl-kids.com/worksheets/choose.html<br></td></tr>
<tr>
