<td><strong>授课对象</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2"></td>
<td><strong>学生信息</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="5"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="3"><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ）&nbsp; </strong><br></td>
<td colspan="6"><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N） </strong></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课目标<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8">
<p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课内容</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8">
<p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课提纲<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8">
<p>&nbsp;Unit&nbsp;3:&nbsp;My&nbsp;Friends</p>
1.  Objective:&nbsp;<br>
Students&nbsp;learn&nbsp;to:<br>
-&nbsp;Describe&nbsp;features&nbsp;of&nbsp;people<br>
-&nbsp;Express&nbsp;preferences<br>
2.  Vocabulary<br>
Friends,&nbsp;strong,&nbsp;thin,&nbsp;quiet,&nbsp;long&nbsp;hair,&nbsp;short&nbsp;hair,&nbsp;big,&nbsp;small,&nbsp;head,&nbsp;eyes,&nbsp;nose,&nbsp;mouth,&nbsp;ears,&nbsp;music,&nbsp;science,&nbsp;sport,&nbsp;computer,&nbsp;painting<br>
3.  Expressions:&nbsp;What&nbsp;is&nbsp;his&nbsp;name?&nbsp;Who&nbsp;is&nbsp;he?&nbsp;I&nbsp;like…&nbsp;<br>
<br>
Content Material  Note<br>
Period&nbsp;1<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.&nbsp;Warm-up&nbsp;(5-10&nbsp;mins)&nbsp;<br>
Revision&nbsp;on&nbsp;school&nbsp;bag&nbsp;items<br>
老师带领全班复习一遍<br>
Chinese&nbsp;book，English&nbsp;book,&nbsp;math&nbsp;book,&nbsp;Story-book,&nbsp;notebook,&nbsp;schoolbag<br>
<br>
How&nbsp;many…&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;have?<br>
I&nbsp;have…<br>
<br>
Pairwork<br>
两个人一组，互相问答今天书包里都有什么<br>
<br>
    <br>
Vocabulary:&nbsp;weather&nbsp;(10-15&nbsp;mins)<br>
按照头发长短，选几位同学，请其它同学翻开Unit&nbsp;3的生词表，猜猜这些都是什么词。然后把这些词写下来，与学生一起巩固复习几遍发音、拼写<br>
（long&nbsp;hair,&nbsp;short&nbsp;hair,&nbsp;big,&nbsp;small,&nbsp;head,&nbsp;eyes,&nbsp;nose,&nbsp;mouth,&nbsp;ears）<br>
<br>
教师说出一个形容词，请同学快速说出它的反义词，看谁的反应快　　<br>
tall-short&nbsp;,long-short&nbsp;,big-small&nbsp;,black-white&nbsp;,red-green,&nbsp;on-under　    <br>
　<br>
复习句型<br>
What&nbsp;is&nbsp;his&nbsp;name?&nbsp;Who&nbsp;is&nbsp;he?&nbsp;I&nbsp;like…&nbsp;<br>
Pairwork    <br>
Period&nbsp;2<br>
Warm-up&nbsp;&nbsp;(15&nbsp;minutes)<br>
复习句型<br>
He/She&nbsp;has&nbsp;____&nbsp;hair,&nbsp;____&nbsp;eyes,&nbsp;____&nbsp;mouth,&nbsp;_____&nbsp;nose.&nbsp;He/she&nbsp;likes&nbsp;music/science/sport,/computer/painting&nbsp;who&nbsp;is&nbsp;he<br>
<br>
2.&nbsp;游戏guess&nbsp;who&nbsp;(15&nbsp;minutes)<br>
找出5－7个杂志上的人物或卡通人物，贴在黑板上。然后对学生形容一个人物，让大家猜<br>
可以作为小组游戏<br>
  Smurfs<br>
Smurfette<br>
Doraemon<br>
kongfu&nbsp;Panda&nbsp;po<br>
Yao<br>
calabash&nbsp;brothers  <br>
<br>
-&nbsp;小活动&nbsp;（15&nbsp;minutes）<br>
请一位学生上台，心中想好班上一个同学。然后说如下几个句子让同学们猜猜这是谁：<br>
He/She&nbsp;has&nbsp;____&nbsp;hair,&nbsp;____&nbsp;eyes,&nbsp;____&nbsp;mouth,&nbsp;_____&nbsp;nose.&nbsp;He/she&nbsp;likes&nbsp;music/science/sport,/computer/painting&nbsp;<br>
Who&nbsp;is&nbsp;he? &nbsp;<br></td></tr>
<tr>
