<TD colSpan=6><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N）</strong></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课目标<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>复习Unit 3</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课内容</strong><BR></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>1. 点名，发name cards <BR>2. 分组 <BR>3. 强调纪律 <BR>4. 复习 <BR>（1） Greetings: <BR>Hi/Hello/Good morning <BR>What’s your name? What’s his name? What’s her name? <BR>My name is…His name is…Her name is… <BR>（2）对话练习（助教） <BR>A: Hi/Hello/Good morning <BR>B: Hi/Hello/Good morning <BR>A: What’s your name? <BR>B: My name is… What’s your name? <BR>A: My name is…What’s his/her name? <BR>B: His/her name is… <BR>5. （1）句型He is… <BR>tall short thin strong fat <BR>跟读：tall, tall, tall, I am/He is/She is tall <BR>（2） 句型He has… <BR>名词：eyes, ears, nose, mouth, hair, face <BR>形容词：big, small, round, long, short,(curly, straight) <BR>跟读，快速猜词etc <BR>在班里挑学生全班一起形容他/她 <BR>6. 复习新单词 <BR>（1） 跟读卡片 <BR>（2） 传话游戏（助教） <BR>每组站起来排成一行，助教将卡片展示给最后的学生，传英文单词。看哪组最快传完。 <BR></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD><strong>授课提纲<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>
<P><BR>&nbsp;</P></TD></TR>
