是否已了解上次课的授课情况&quot;;&quot;<div class="hdwiki_tmml">第一次活动</div>
<p>
<table class="table" width="100%" align="left">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>上课准备提纲</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>志愿者信息</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>备课人</strong><br></td>
<td>dyinginthesun</td>
<td><strong>Email/MSN</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="3">chris_tomato@hotmail.com</td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>所属课程组</strong><br></td>
<td>英语</td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>课程信息</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>课程名称</strong><br></td>
<td>U1&nbsp;My&nbsp;New&nbsp;Teachers</td>
<td><strong>上课日期</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">2011/9/17</td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>上课时长</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">分钟<br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课对象</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">五年级</td>
<td><strong>学生信息</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="5"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="3"><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ）</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="6"><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N）</strong></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课目标<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8"></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课内容</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8">S1.&nbsp;点名，发name&nbsp;cards&nbsp;（需助教）<br>
S2.&nbsp;分组&nbsp;（需助教）<br>
S3.&nbsp;课堂规则<br>
S4.&nbsp;学生自我介绍&nbsp;（视情况）：My&nbsp;name&nbsp;is______.&nbsp;I'm&nbsp;____&nbsp;years&nbsp;old.&nbsp;I'm&nbsp;from&nbsp;______.<br>
S5.&nbsp;复习：“Me&nbsp;too”教师依次说一下五个句子，符合其所描述情况的学生站起来说&nbsp;"Me&nbsp;too!"<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.&nbsp;I'm&nbsp;a&nbsp;girl.&nbsp;2.&nbsp;I'm&nbsp;from&nbsp;Hebei.&nbsp;3.&nbsp;I&nbsp;have&nbsp;a&nbsp;colourful&nbsp;skirt.&nbsp;4.&nbsp;I&nbsp;like&nbsp;sheep.&nbsp;5.&nbsp;I&nbsp;like&nbsp;music.<br>
S6.&nbsp;新课内容：<br>
1.&nbsp;&nbsp;科目：以Do&nbsp;you&nbsp;have&nbsp;music&nbsp;classes&nbsp;at&nbsp;school?&nbsp;为过渡，再问学校中还有什么课程,先由学生自己说，再由学生写在黑板上。（English,&nbsp;Chinese,&nbsp;Math,&nbsp;Music,&nbsp;P.E,&nbsp;Science,&nbsp;Art...)<br>
2.&nbsp;&nbsp;形容词：(young,&nbsp;funny,&nbsp;tall,&nbsp;strong,&nbsp;kind,&nbsp;old,&nbsp;short,&nbsp;thin,&nbsp;quiet,&nbsp;strict,&nbsp;smart,&nbsp;active,&nbsp;fun,&nbsp;beautiful/pretty,&nbsp;heavy/large...)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1)&nbsp;以Brainstorm形式呈现<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2)&nbsp;领读，跟读<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3）学生将所有形容词以反义词/对比词形式分类，并将中英文写在笔记本上&nbsp;（需助教）<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4）小组内一起练习&nbsp;（需助教）<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;5）复习：老师说中文，学生说英文，再反过来复习<br>
3.&nbsp;&nbsp;描述Christine:&nbsp;She&nbsp;is&nbsp;______.&nbsp;She&nbsp;is&nbsp;_____&nbsp;and&nbsp;______.&nbsp;She&nbsp;is&nbsp;_____&nbsp;but&nbsp;______.<br>
4.&nbsp;&nbsp;Quessing&nbsp;Game:&nbsp;猜学校的老师<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1）每组选学校里的一位老师描述，按下列句式写下来，一人一句：Mr./Miss./Ms.(&nbsp;教区别）______is&nbsp;our&nbsp;______&nbsp;teacher.&nbsp;She/He's&nbsp;____________.&nbsp;（需助教）<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2）其他两组学生在3分钟内提问问题：Is&nbsp;she/he&nbsp;________?&nbsp;问题仅限外貌或性格<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3）看哪组学生能猜出是哪位老师或教哪一科，猜对的给小组加一个笑脸<br>
5.&nbsp;&nbsp;对话练习：（需助教）<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Who&nbsp;is&nbsp;your&nbsp;_______&nbsp;teacher?<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mr./Miss./Ms.&nbsp;_____&nbsp;is&nbsp;our/my&nbsp;_______&nbsp;teacher.<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;What&nbsp;is&nbsp;she/he&nbsp;like?<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;She/He&nbsp;is&nbsp;_______.&nbsp;<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
<br>
<br>
<br><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课提纲<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>教学环境、材料需求</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8"></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>助教需求<br></strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8"></td></tr></tbody></table><br></p>
<p><br>&nbsp;</p>
<p><br>&nbsp;</p>
<div class="hdwiki_tmml">第二次活动</div>
<br>
<p>
<table class="table" width="100%" align="left">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>上课准备提纲</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>志愿者信息</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>备课人</strong><br></td>
<td>dyinginthesun<br></td>
<td><strong>Email/MSN</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="3">chris_tomato@hotmail.com<br></td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>所属课程组</strong><br></td>
<td>英语<br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>课程信息</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>课程名称</strong><br></td>
<td>U1 My New Teachers<br></td>
<td><strong>上课日期</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">9月24日<br></td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>上课时长</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">50分钟<br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课对象</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">五年级<br></td>
<td><strong>学生信息</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="5"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="3"><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ）Y</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="6"><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N）N</strong></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课目标<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8"></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课内容</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8">S1.&nbsp;点名，发名片卡<br>
S2.&nbsp;强调纪律<br>
S3.&nbsp;复习：<br>
1.  描述新老师黑曜:&nbsp;She&nbsp;is_______.&nbsp;<br>
2.  Name&nbsp;Game:&nbsp;My&nbsp;name&nbsp;is&nbsp;ME!&nbsp;学生在纸上竖着写下组成自己名字的英文字母（大写），再从学过或知道的形容词中找出含有这些字母的词写下来。看看自己的名字包含了哪些性格密码。例如：Christine&nbsp; （助教参与）<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;
aCtive<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;
Healthy<br>&nbsp;&nbsp; stRict&nbsp;<br>
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; Interesting<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Smart<br>
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; Thin<br>beautIful<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Nice<br>&nbsp; lovEly<br>
展示：My&nbsp;name&nbsp;is&nbsp;______.&nbsp;I’m&nbsp;_______.<br>
3.  扩充新词：以图片形式呈现<br>
4.  句型练习：（助教参与）<br>1)&nbsp;对话<br>
A:&nbsp;Who&nbsp;is&nbsp;your______&nbsp;teacher?<br>
B:&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;/Miss.&nbsp;/Ms.&nbsp;___&nbsp;is&nbsp;my&nbsp;_______&nbsp;teacher.<br>
A:&nbsp;What&nbsp;is&nbsp;he/she&nbsp;like?<br>
B:&nbsp;He/She&nbsp;is&nbsp;very&nbsp;______.&nbsp;<br>
<br>
2)&nbsp;小组活动<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;A:&nbsp;Do&nbsp;you&nbsp;have&nbsp;new&nbsp;teachers?<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;C,D:&nbsp;We&nbsp;have&nbsp;___&nbsp;new&nbsp;teachers.<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;B:&nbsp;Who&nbsp;are&nbsp;they?<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;C:&nbsp;A/an&nbsp;_____&nbsp;teacher,&nbsp;a/an&nbsp;____&nbsp;teacher,&nbsp;…<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;A:&nbsp;Who&nbsp;is&nbsp;your&nbsp;_____&nbsp;teacher?<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;D:&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;/Miss.&nbsp;/Ms.&nbsp;___&nbsp;is&nbsp;our&nbsp;_______&nbsp;teacher.<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;B:&nbsp;What&nbsp;is&nbsp;he/she&nbsp;like?<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;C:&nbsp;He/She&nbsp;is&nbsp;______&nbsp;and&nbsp;______.<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;B:&nbsp;Who&nbsp;is&nbsp;your&nbsp;_____&nbsp;teacher?<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;C:&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;/Miss.&nbsp;/Ms.&nbsp;___&nbsp;is&nbsp;our&nbsp;_______&nbsp;teacher.<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;A:&nbsp;What&nbsp;is&nbsp;he/she&nbsp;like?<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;D:&nbsp;He/She&nbsp;is&nbsp;______&nbsp;but&nbsp;______.<br>&nbsp;
<br><br></td></tr>
<tr>
