<td colspan="2"><strong>所属课程组</strong><br></td>
<td>英语</td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>课程信息</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>课程名称 音乐课</strong><br></td>
<td>U2 My days of the week</td>
<td><strong>上课日期</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">10.15</td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>上课时长</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">100分钟<br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课对象</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">五年级</td>
<td><strong>学生信息</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="5"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="3"><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ） &nbsp;Y</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="6"><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N）N</strong></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课目标<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8">1. 复习之前所学知识；2. 结束U2</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课内容</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8">S1.&nbsp;Test:&nbsp;听中文写英文、听英文写中文<br>
年轻的、安静的、严格的、聪明的、活跃的/积极的、瘦的、有趣的/好笑的<br>
beautiful/pretty、healthy、friendly<br>
S2.&nbsp;Revision:<br>
1.&nbsp;游戏：&nbsp;学生分为两组，站成两列。第一个学生向第二个学生用手指表示一个数字（1-7）并提问：What&nbsp;day&nbsp;is&nbsp;it&nbsp;today?&nbsp;第二个学生回答，依次类推，知道最后一个学生回答完。在规定时间内最先完成的小组胜。<br>
注意事项：<br>
1)&nbsp;相邻的两组问答不能重复数字，可以各一个重复一个数字，但整组下来不能重复超过2次；<br>
2)&nbsp;需助教担当评委，监督学生问答是否正确，并按照上述规则进行游戏；<br>
3)&nbsp;强调区分Tuesday&nbsp;和Thursday:&nbsp;Tuesday&nbsp;(2s);&nbsp;Thursday&nbsp;(4&nbsp;si-th)。<br>
2.&nbsp;&nbsp;Pairwork:&nbsp;“设计属于你自己的课表”<br>
A:&nbsp;What&nbsp;day&nbsp;is&nbsp;it&nbsp;today?<br>
B:&nbsp;It’s&nbsp;_______.<br>
A:&nbsp;What&nbsp;class&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;have&nbsp;on&nbsp;_______s?<br>
&nbsp;B:&nbsp;We&nbsp;have&nbsp;____________.<br>
A:&nbsp;&nbsp;Who&nbsp;is&nbsp;your&nbsp;_______&nbsp;teacher?<br>
B:&nbsp;&nbsp;Mr./Miss/Ms.&nbsp;____&nbsp;is&nbsp;our&nbsp;_______&nbsp;teacher.<br>
A:&nbsp;&nbsp;What&nbsp;is&nbsp;she/he&nbsp;like?<br>
B:&nbsp;&nbsp;She/He&nbsp;is__________.&nbsp;(&nbsp;very,&nbsp;and,&nbsp;but)<br>
给每对学生一张带有数字的卡片（1-7），代表一周的7天，学生根据手中卡片上的数字结合学过的内容编对话，设计一天的课程。<br>
S2.&nbsp;新授课:&nbsp;What&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;do&nbsp;on&nbsp;weekends?<br>
1.&nbsp;头脑风暴：do&nbsp;homework/watch&nbsp;TV/read&nbsp;books/play&nbsp;computer&nbsp;games/paint/play&nbsp;ping-pong/basketball/football/badminton/do&nbsp;sports/do&nbsp;housework/have&nbsp;LEAD&nbsp;classes…<br>
2.&nbsp;游戏：1个学生上讲台根据自己所抽的卡片上的词组表演该动作，其余学生猜。<br>
3.&nbsp;Pairwork:&nbsp;What&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;do&nbsp;on&nbsp;Saturdays/&nbsp;Sundays?&nbsp;&nbsp;I&nbsp;often&nbsp;__________________.<br>
4.&nbsp;游戏：Find&nbsp;your&nbsp;friend!<br>
学生先写下自己周六和周日喜欢做的事情，然后在全班互相提问&nbsp;“Do&nbsp;you&nbsp;______&nbsp;on_____s?”&nbsp;记下回答”Yes,&nbsp;I&nbsp;do”的学生名字，最后做report:&nbsp;I&nbsp;can&nbsp;__________&nbsp;with&nbsp;________&nbsp;on&nbsp;Saturdays.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;I&nbsp;can&nbsp;__________&nbsp;with&nbsp;________&nbsp;on&nbsp;Sundays.<br>
S3.&nbsp;Miss&nbsp;Cat’s&nbsp;week<br>
要求学生根据这两个单元所学内容编故事。<br>
提示：Miss&nbsp;Cat&nbsp;is__________________.<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; She&nbsp;has/likes/does&nbsp;_____________.<br></td></tr>
<tr>
