<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>上课准备提纲</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>志愿者信息</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>备课人</strong><br></td>
<td>dyinginthesun<br></td>
<td><strong>Email/MSN</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="3">chris_tomato@hotmail.com<br></td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>所属课程组</strong><br></td>
<td>英语<br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="9">
<p align="center"><strong>课程信息</strong></p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>课程名称</strong><br></td>
<td>U5 My&nbsp;New&nbsp;Room</td>
<td><strong>上课日期</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">Nov 26<br></td>
<td colspan="2"><strong>上课时长</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2"></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课对象</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="2">五年级<br></td>
<td><strong>学生信息</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="5"><br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="3"><strong>是否已了解上次课的授课情况（Y ） Y</strong></td>
<td colspan="6"><strong>本次课的教案是重复使用已有教案吗（N）N</strong></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课目标<br></strong></td>
<td colspan="8">结束U5<br>1. 学生熟练掌握课本中不同房间及各物品的说法。认识补充的新单词；<br>2. 熟练掌握There is/are的句型；<br>3. 熟练掌握方位词的用法。<br></td></tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>授课内容</strong><br></td>
<td colspan="8">S1. 室外分组游戏：(助教协助分发图片)<br>1.给每个学生发一张表示家内物品的单词图片(互相之间不能看）（以课本出现单词为主），根据物品摆放的房间，持有放在同一房间的物品单词的学生为一组，2分钟内迅速寻找同伴结组。<br>2. 事先在地上 画个房子轮廓。将写有不同房间类型的单词卡片放在不同区域内。学生每组站在相应位置上。<br>3. 学生组内练习所持物品单词，并一起领读。（助教帮忙）<br>S2.&nbsp; 回到教室中：每个学生发另外一套图片（有些学生可能会拿到只有图片的卡片，有些会拿到只有单词的卡片，并且有的是一个图片对应两张单词卡片，或一个单词卡片对应两张图片，分别在不同学生手中）每个学生大声念出自己手中的物品名称，手中拿着一样物品卡片的两个学生抢答，先答对者胜，为该组加一个笑脸。（单词以课本外为主）<br>S3. Introduce your room.<br>1. 句型： There&nbsp;is&nbsp;a /an _____&nbsp;in&nbsp;my&nbsp;_________. 每个学生将手中的图片贴在黑板上的房子里的不同房间内，并以此句型造句。<br>2. 句型： A: What's in your ______ room? B: There are ____&nbsp; _____s in my ________. 学生根据不同房间内所贴物品的数量做对话。<br>S4. Design your own room: <br>1. 黑板分为5个区域，每组将想放在自己代表的房间的物品图片，贴在相应区域内的不同位置。<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 老师提问： Where is <span style="font-weight: bold;">the </span>______? 引导学生回答It's _________.----重复：The ____ is __________.<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Where are <span style="font-weight: bold;">the</span> ________s? 引导学生回答 They're _________.----重复： The _____s are ________.<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 方位词： in (eg. in the ____ room)/near/on/in front of/behind/under/over (a picture over the bed)<br>2. 接龙： This is a ______ 方位词 <span style="font-weight: bold;">the</span> ________.&nbsp; There are 数词______ s 方位词 <span style="font-weight: bold;">the</span> _______. 老师指定图片，学生造句<br>3. 小组活动： （助教可协助）<br>必须出现的句型： <br>This is a picture of our room. <br>There is a ____ 方位词&nbsp;the&nbsp;________.&nbsp; <br>There&nbsp;are&nbsp;数词______&nbsp;s&nbsp;方位词&nbsp;the&nbsp;_______. <br>The ______ is/are _________.<br>What's 方位词 the ________? There is a _______ 方位词 the ________/ There are 数词 ______s 方位词 the _______.<br>I _________ in my _______ room.<br>可以自己加句子。<br>report 时组内一人说一句<br>S5. Test: Christine's house<br>老师念句子，学生根据描述画图。(要求学生画大点）<br>Christine has a new flat. It's on the third floor. （前两句不用画） There are 2 bedrooms, a living room, a dining room, a kichen and a bathroom.(在所画房子内标出房间名称） There is an end table in the bedroom. There is book on the end table.&nbsp; There are 2 chairs in the dining room. There is a table near the chairs. There is a sofa in the living room. There is a TV in front of the sofa. There are 2 curtains in the bathroom. There is a mirror behind the curtains. There is a closet in the kichen. There are 2 trash bins under the closet.<br></td></tr>
