<TR>
<TD><strong>授课提纲<BR></strong></TD>
<TD colSpan=8>Unit 1 How do you go there? <BR>第一课，基础 <BR>1. 通过某交通工具到达某处 <BR>1）Go to school/Go to bus stop/Go to the park/Go there/Go home <BR>Come to my home/Come home <BR>2）By bike/plane/bus/subway/ship/train/car/taxi <BR>On foot/Walk to…/Walk there <BR>2. Greeting and Goodbye <BR>1）Hello/Hi/Hey, <BR>How are you? <BR>How are you doing? <BR>How are you doing today/recently? <BR>How is going? <BR>What’s up? <BR>后面可以接 name/man/buddy/dude <BR>2）（I’ll）See you ( later/ around/then) <BR>3. Floor <BR>一楼：ground floor/first floor <BR>地下室：Basement：B1/B2 <BR>4. Traffic <BR>1）Traffic light/Traffic rule/Traffic jam/Or simple traffic <BR>Stop at the red light/Wait at a yellow light/Go at a green light <BR>2）Crosswalk 人行横道 <BR>3）One way 单行道 <BR>4）No entry 此路不通 <BR>5. Mean <BR>1）意味着，表示什么的意思 <BR>2）刻薄的 <BR>Meaning：意思，含义 <BR>Meaningful：有意义的 <BR>Meaningless：无意义的 <BR><BR>第二课，拓展 <BR>6. 发音 <BR>7. Restaurant and Food <BR>1) American Restaurant： <BR>--Fast Food Restaurant <BR>Kentucky Fried Chicken 肯塔基州炸鸡 <BR>McDonald's 麦当劳 <BR>Burger King 汉堡王 <BR>Pizza Hut 必胜客 <BR>French Fry（French Fries） （法式）炸薯条 <BR>Cola：Coca Cola/Pepsi <BR>Sprite [spraɪt] /7-Up <BR>--Bar and Grill 烤肉酒店？（×）带餐厅的酒吧 （√） <BR>--Beer/Wine/Liquor <BR>--Bar Food: Steak/Fish and Fry/Burger/Sandwich/Salad/Pizza <BR>2) Italian/French/Mexican/Chinese/Japanese Restaurant <BR>--Pasta：Spaghetti 实心粉/Macaroni 通心粉 <BR>Lazania 千层面 <BR>--French Snail/Goose Liver/French toast <BR>--Taco/Tamale[tə'mɑlɪ] <BR>--Gongbao Chicken/Muxu Meat <BR>--Sushi/Instant noddles <BR>3）Coffee Shop/Costa Coffee/Starbucks <BR>-- Black黑咖啡/Latte 拿铁/ Cappuccino卡布奇诺 <BR>-- Black Tea 红茶/Green Tea 绿茶 <BR>-- Milk Shake 奶昔 <BR>-- Muffin 松饼/Cupcake <BR><BR></TD></TR>
